(106, 10, '人机互动触摸屏解决方案', 'The man-machine interactive touchscreens solutions ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '   触摸屏人机交互简单，且可以有丰富多彩的多媒体展示，图文声茂，生动活泼。\r\n触摸屏按照尺寸来分，有两种：小屏（17、19英寸普屏/宽屏）、大屏（40英寸以上宽屏）。小屏适用于一般环境，而大屏则由于它的外观形象好、气质高而普遍用于需要彰显高贵气派的环境下。 VR技术用于触摸屏，这是一种十分实用的使用方式。比起传统的图片和文字介绍，它能够带给我们更多的更完整的信息。我们将以一种独特的视角来观察眼前的一切，轻松的操控鼠标就可以控制画面中的物体。这是一种奇特的指尖上的虚拟世界。\r\n她具有触摸屏的特性：操作简单，外形美观，功能强大，兼容性好，应用范围广。\r\n\r\n除此以外，她还具有以下功能：\r\n    1.可以对事物进行720°全方位自由参看；\r\n    2.可以对物体任意缩放；\r\n    3.可以表现事物的整体和局部，表现力强，自由度高；\r\n    4.事物的说明讲解可以随客户的意愿触发； 5.可以连接数据库，事物的信息（如：价格）会随客户的选配而更改；\r\n    6.事物的历史、作用、外形、配件、颜色、价格、说明等信息都可以与后台数据库相连，方便日后维护更新；\r\n    7.客户可以随意挑选事物的型号、颜色、外壳，可以随意挑选配件然后组装，效果实时显示，功能实时更新；\r\n    8.客户可以任意对产品使用体验；\r\n\r\n拓展功能：\r\n    1.和大屏立体显示系统搭配：这将为整个系统增加震撼的视觉效果。特别是和裸眼立体显示器搭配，可以用于各种展览展示。\r\n    2.和操纵杆、3D球、方向盘等外设搭配：这将使得漫游和转动事物的操作变得更加的灵活、方便。\r\n\r\n她具有以下优势：\r\n    1.她能够降低费用。\r\n    她的制作费用低。一般的VR内容仅仅相当于几分之一全景图的价钱（两张效果图的价钱）却可以发挥比全景图更强大的功能。\r\n    2.她服务态度好，讲解详细。\r\n    每个产品每个部件都会“说话”，都能够自动介绍自己，都能够让人全方位的观看自己（还能够局部放大），提供试用功能，还提供细腻的使用指导。  24小时不知疲倦的提供生动的、主动的、全面而周到的服务。\r\n    3.她能够让信息传递更加的生动、简单、明了。\r\n    4.她能够提供全面的服务。\r\n    5.她具有相当的智能化，能够发挥计算机的高速运算能力，具有判断和搜索功能，能够代替部分人力工作。\r\n\r\n我们的技术优势：\r\n    1.可以建立模型数据库，方便模型的更新和替换。\r\n    2.拓展功能强。核心VR内容可以嵌入WEB、PPT、Flash（或者其他程序）；还可以用于平面/立体投影展示、桌面式立体显示、立体显示器。支持操纵杆、3D球、方向盘等外设。\r\n    3.针对特殊的外设，我们可以开发硬件接口程序。\r\n    4.程序文件小，运行画面流畅。\r\n    5.制作经验丰富。长期的制作经验，让我们所制作的内容无论从色彩上、设计上还是技术上都是最出色的。\r\n\r\n ', 'Touch human-machine interaction is simple, and can be a rich and colorful multimedia display, graphic acoustic metallocene, lively.\r\n\r\nTouch screen size to points, according to have two kinds: small screen (17, 19 inch widescreen), PuBing/DaBing (40 inches above the widescreen). Small screens used in general environment, and DaBing is because of its appearance, good temperament and widely used to need high reveals high air environment. VR technology used for touch screen, this is a very practical use way. Compared to traditional images and text introduction, it can bring us more more complete information. We will with a unique visual Angle to observe all, easy sight of manipulating mouse can control the picture objects. This is a peculiar finger on the virtual world.\r\n\r\nShe has a touch screen characteristics: the operation is simple, beautiful shape, powerful, good compatibility, application scope.\r\n\r\nIn addition, she also has the following functions:\r\n\r\n1 ° to things for free see 720 omni-directional;\r\n\r\n2. Can of object caling;\r\n\r\n3. Can show the overall and local things, strong expressiveness, freedom high;\r\n\r\n4. Things with the customer that willingness to explain can trigger; 5. Can connect to database, the information (such as: something with customer price change; selection\r\n\r\n6. Things history, function, appearance, accessories, color, price, instruction information can be connected with the backend database, convenient in maintenance update;\r\n\r\n7. Customers can choose at will things model, color, shell, be good at choosing accessories and assembly, the effect is real-time display real-time updates, function;\r\n\r\n8. Customers can any use of the product experience;\r\n\r\nExpand functions:\r\n\r\n1. And DaBing stereoscopic displays collocation: this will increase for the entire system shock visual effect. Especially and department.forward is tie-in, can be used for three-dimensional display various exhibition.\r\n\r\n2. And joysticks, 3D ball, steering wheel peripherals like collocation: this will allow roaming and rotating the operation of the things become more flexible, convenient.\r\n\r\nShe has the following advantages:\r\n\r\n1. She can reduce costs.\r\n\r\nHer production cost is low. General VR content only equivalent to fractions of a panorama price (the price of two pieces of rendering), can play more powerful than panorama function.\r\n\r\n2. She good attitude, the explanation is detailed.\r\n\r\nEach product each component will be "talk", are able to automatically to introduce myself, can let a person omni-directional watch yourself (also can provide partial enlargement), try functions, but also provide exquisite instructions. 24 hours tireless provides vivid and active, comprehensive and the thorough service.\r\n\r\n3. She can make information more vivid, simple, clear.\r\n\r\n4. She can provide comprehensive service.\r\n\r\n5. She is quite intelligent, can play a computer''s high-speed operation ability, has the judgment and search function, can replace part human work.\r\n\r\nOur technical advantage:\r\n\r\n1. Can build model database, convenient model updating and replace.\r\n\r\n2. Develop strong function. Core VR content can be embedded WEB, PPT, Flash (or other programs); Can also be used for plane/stereo projection display, desktop type stereo display, three-dimensional display. Support joystick, 3D ball, steering wheel etc peripherals.\r\n\r\n3. According to special peripherals, we can develop the hardware interface program.\r\n\r\n4. Program files small, smooth running picture.\r\n\r\n5. Make the rich in experience. Long-term production experience, let us make content on colour, design whether from all still technology are the most outstanding. ', '../pic/2011052370924_1_110425114608_1.jpg', '人机互动触摸屏解决方案', 'The man-machine interactive touchscreens solutions ', '', 33),
(107, 10, '多通道解决方案', 'Multichannel solutions ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '     多通道环幕（立体）投影系统是指采用多台投影机组合而成的多通道大屏幕展示系统，它比普通的标准投影系统具备更大的显示尺寸、更宽的视野、更多的显示内容、更高的显示分辨率，以及更具冲击力和沉浸感的视觉效果。\r\n     其具有一定弧度的巨幅显示空间包围了所有参与者的整个观看视野，再配合环绕立体声响系统，可使仿真参与者充分体验一种高度身临其境的三维立体视听感受，获得一个具有高度沉浸感的虚拟仿真可视协同环境。\r\n\r\n在众多的虚拟仿真显示系统中多通道环幕投影是一个技术含量极高的显示系统，需要有以下几项强有力的核心技术做支撑：\r\n\r\n \r\n     数字几何矫正（即非线性失真矫正）技术\r\n     多通道视景同步控制技术\r\n     数字图像边缘融合技术\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n【硬件配置为】\r\n投影幕尺寸\r\n     根据环形幕半径的大小，通常为120 、135、180、240、270、360度弧度不等。注:也可根据要求订制。\r\n投影方式：\r\n     正投 或 背投/平面 或 立体 \r\n通道个数：\r\n     我们将根据您的实际环幕尺寸、投影比例（4：3 或是16：9）、投影画面效果等信息计算通道个数（也就是画面个数）。\r\n投影机：\r\n     我们将根据通道个数及投影方式来选择投影机个数\r\n     我们将根据投影环境、画面效果要求来选择投影机的参数\r\n边缘融合：\r\n     软件融合 或 硬件融合\r\n     我们推荐使用硬件融合，适用性广，画面效果好，性能稳定。硬件融合也是目前市场的主流选择。\r\n【支持的播放格式】\r\n软件融合：\r\n    她除了能播放普通平面影片之外，还能将立体影片、VR内容、3D游戏用立体投影的方式显示出来，给人逼真震撼的视觉享受。\r\n硬件融合：\r\n    对播放的文件格式无限制。支持平面、立体等显示方式\r\n    高清（最高支持2048×1536）、高刷新率（35~75Hz）。能够播放动作片而画面无迟钝、无延迟。\r\n【技术优势】\r\n系统性能：\r\n   系统调整方便快捷，系统稳定，性能好（高清，高刷新率，边缘融合带肉眼不可视）；引进国外领先的立体显示技术，立体可视化范围大、角度宽，立体效果好，立体沉浸感强，而且不会造成眼睛长时间观看疲劳。\r\n能够提供优质的内容制作服务、模拟器制作服务：\r\n包括：动画的制作、立体影片的制作、室内/外建筑漫游内容的制作、三维地理信息内容制作、模拟驾驶器的制作、模拟训练平台的制作。\r\n\r\n【适用领域】\r\n  教育训练科研、展览展示、增强型虚拟仿真。\r\n\r\n\r\n【可用作】\r\n    教学、会议、创造虚拟空间、模拟训练、模拟驾驶、虚拟小区漫游、城市规划、三维地理信息、立体视频播放、电影播放等。', 'Multichannel HuanMu (3d) projection system is refers to using multiple projector with a combination of multi-channel big screen display system, it than ordinary standard projection system has greater display size, wider vision, more show content, the higher the display resolution, and more powerful and immersed sense of visual effect.\r\n\r\nIt has certain radian display space surrounded the huge vision of all participants, coupled with the watch around stereo sound system, which can make the simulation participants fully experience a highly immersive 3d audio-visual feeling, the obtained a highly immersed sense of visual collaborative virtual simulation environment.\r\n\r\nIn many of the virtual simulation display systems HuanMu projection is a multi-channel high technical content of the display system, need to have the following several strong core technology do support:\r\n\r\nDigital geometric correction (namely nonlinear distortion correction) technology\r\n\r\nMultichannel visual synchronous control technology\r\n\r\nDigital image edge fusion technique\r\n\r\n【 hardware configuration for 】\r\n\r\nProjection screen size\r\n\r\nAccording to the size of the annular act radius, usually 120, 135, 180, 240, 270, 360-degree radian dollars. Note: also can specially according to the requirement.\r\n\r\nProjection mode:\r\n\r\nAre cast or over-head projectors/two-dimensional or three-dimensional\r\n\r\nChannel number:\r\n\r\nWe will HuanMu according to your actual size, the projection proportion (4:3 or 16:9), projection screen effect of information is also calculated the number (picture channel array.\r\n\r\nThe projector:\r\n\r\nWe will according to the channel number and projection way to select the projector number\r\n\r\nWe will depending on projective environment, visually requirements to choose the projector parameters\r\n\r\nEdge fusion:\r\n\r\nSoftware fusion or hardware fusion\r\n\r\nWe recommend using hardware fusion, applicability, wide, screen effect is good, stable performance. Is the current market hardware fusion mainstream choice.\r\n\r\n【 support format 】\r\n\r\nSoftware fusion:\r\n\r\nShe besides can play ordinary plane film besides, still can will stereoscopic films, VR content, 3D game the way with 3D projection display, give a person the visual enjoyment. Lifelike shock\r\n\r\nHardware fusion:\r\n\r\nTo play the file format unlimited. Support such as plane, 3-d showing the way\r\n\r\nHd (maximum support 2048 x stable), high refresh rate (35 ~ 75Hz). Can play action movies while the picture no dull, without delay.\r\n\r\n【 technology advantage 】\r\n\r\nThe system performance:\r\n\r\nSystem adjustment conveniently, the system is stable, good performance (hd, high refresh rate, edge with macroscopic invisible fusion); Introducing foreign advanced 3d display technologies, three-dimensional visual range, Angle wide, stereoscopic effect is good, solid immersed sense of strong, and won''t cause eyes long time watching fatigue.\r\n\r\nTo provide quality content production services, simulator production services:\r\n\r\nIncluding: animation production, three-dimensional film production, indoor/out construction roaming content production, 3d geographic information content production, and the manufacture of the simulated driving device simulation training platform production.\r\n\r\n【 applicable field 】\r\n\r\nEducation training research, exhibition, enhanced virtual simulation.\r\n\r\n【 can be used as 】\r\n\r\nTeaching, meetings, create virtual space, simulated training, simulated driving, virtual community roaming, city planning, 3d, stereo video playback geographical information, showing movies, etc. ', '../pic/2011052338759_vrcase_9.jpg', '多通道解决方案', 'Multichannel solutions ', '', 15),
(108, 0, '自动化学院召开2008级中加项目同学交流座谈会', 'Level of automation of adding project at the 2008 classmates forum', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '自08级中加分流同学到自动化学院学习已有一年时间，为让中加同学更好地适应新学院的学习生活，了解同学们近一年学习、思想和生活中的具体问题及困难，自动化学院特召开中加同学交流座谈会。\r\n\r\n5月19日上午8点，座谈会在学院会议室进行。学院分管教学的胡向东副院长、分管学生工作的邓素碧副书记、08级辅导员谭静老师及所有08级中加班同学都参加了座谈会。\r\n\r\n会议之初，胡院长就我院对中加分流同学的培养方案对同学们进行了细致的解读，并且结合一些同学提出的关于培养方案内的课程设置、模块学分、毕业相关要求等问题进行了耐心的解答。之后，邓书记就同学们提出的中加同学的个人发展方面的困惑等都做出了解答，包括中加同学的个人职业生涯规划发展、入党等相关问题。\r\n\r\n会上，每位同学都畅所欲言，就自己进入到自动化学院学习这一年来进行了总结，包括思想上、学习中以及生活上的一些收获、不适应及困惑，希望借助学院、老师给予帮助和改进的方面。座谈会在同学们热烈的交流中结束。\r\n\r\n这次交流座谈会的召开，获得中加同学的普遍欢迎。也体现了我院对于各类学生在统一培养的过程中进行分类指导的思想，包括为中加分流同学根据他们前两年的学习情况制定适用于他们的后两年专业培养计划、在组织发展中在中加同学中发展优秀同学等一系列关怀。希望在接下来的工作中，发扬良好的，改进不足的，让中加分流同学在我院都能有好的发展和成绩。', 'Add the shunt classmate to 2008 levels of automation of learning for one year time, adding to let students better adapt to new college study life, know the students study, thought and nearly a year, the concrete problems and difficulties life, automation academy add classmates symposium held.\r\n\r\nMay 19, 8 a.m., symposium in college conference room. College HuXiangDong vice President in charge of teaching DengSuBi charge students'' work, vice secretary of TanJing teacher grade counselors, 08 2008 levels of overtime, and all students attended the forum.\r\n\r\nAt the beginning of the meeting, hu dean is our classmates to shunt the training program to add detail for students, and combine the reading some students put on within the cultivation plan curriculum, module credits, graduation requirements such issues as patient answer. DengShuJi just after the classmates add classmates put forward the personal development such as the confused has made answer, including china-canada classmate personal career planning development and problems related to recruiting.\r\n\r\nThe meeting, each students speak freely, oneself into automation college this years are summarized, including the thought, study and life on some of the harvest, does not adapt and puzzles, hope that through college, the teacher give help and improved. Symposium on the classmates warm exchange ended.\r\n\r\nThis exchange symposium held, add classmate of popular obtained. Also embodies the unity of our students in training for the process of the classified guidance thoughts, including adding shunt students for their first two years of study according to applicable to their conditions to develop the professional training plan, two years after the group developing in developing add classmate a series of excellent students care. Hope in the next work, develop good, improve insufficient, let our classmates add shunt in can have good development and achievement. ', '', '', '', '', 21),
(109, 0, '我校应邀参加2011年重庆市科技活动周活动', 'Our', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '5月15日上午，以“携手建设创新型城市—走近科学、体验科技，走进民众、普惠民生”为主题的2011年重庆市科技活动周在重庆市人民大礼堂广场开幕。\r\n\r\n我校自动化学院网络化控制与智能仪器仪表教育部重点实验室应邀参加了本次科技活动，在科普互动区向前来参观的广大市民展示了通过手机、电脑远程控制现代家居的窗帘、灯光、风扇、门磁、温湿度环境参数等智能家居系统及工业物联网应用科技成果，让广大市民亲身体验了智能家居将带给日常生活的安全、舒适和便捷，深受广大市民的称赞，也深深吸引了重庆电视台等多家新闻媒体的关注。重庆电视台记者在展区现场亲身体验了智能家居系统后，专程到学校制作了新闻专题报道，并在黄金时段播出。', 'May 15th morning, constructing innovative city hand in hand with "-- scientific approach, experience technology, walked into people, PuHuiMin life" as the theme of the 2011 in chongqing people''s HuoDongZhou chongqing science opens the auditorium square\r\n\r\nOur school of automation of networked control and intelligent instruments the key laboratory were invited to this technology activities, in popular science interact area to visiting the general public shows through mobile phones, computers remote control the curtain of contemporary household, lamplight, fan, gate magnetism, temperature and humidity environment parameters, such as intelligent household systems and industrial and technological achievements thing networking application experience, so that the general public intelligent household will bring daily life safe, comfortable and convenient, deeply the general public praise, also deeply attracted chongqing television and a number of news media attention. Chongqing TV reporter in exhibition intelligent household on-site experience, coming to school after system made news special report, and prime time TV. ', '', '', '', '', 12),
(110, 0, '我校参加美国智能电网标准制订工作', 'Our school join the United States intelligence network standard formulating work', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '2011年3月28日至31日我校自动化学院教师严冬博士参加了在美国田纳西州纳什维尔市举行的美国标准化技术委员会（NIST）智能电网互操作平台（SGIP）标准制定工作会议。我校自动化学院共有8位专家参加SGIP工作组的标准化工作。该工作组是应美国国家战略目标中有关智能电网的能源独立与安全法案（EISA）成立的。其工作重点是研究和发布EISA中智能电网的相关标准、信息架构和测试与认证体系。其目标是构建先进的电力系统使能量和信息能够双向互联互通，并且能够提升光能、风能及其它可再生能源的利用率。其涉及范围从家庭用电到输电、变电、配电，再到发电与储能等多个电力领域。\r\n\r\nSGIP组织架构如图所示，其中Governing Board，SGIP Officers和NIST是SGIP的管理者，负责协调和平衡各技术领域标准之间的关系，以及智能电网标准与传统电网标准之间的关系。在SGIP工作组运行过程中，两个标准化委员会（SGAC和SGTCC）和一个标准化工作组（CSWG）是其技术领导核心。其中SGAC主要讨论将智能电网一个宽泛的领域，从技术角度、应用角度和经济运行角度细分为若干个子领域，以方便各个领域的技术人员讨论。SGTCC是探讨对应每个技术标准如何测试和认证。CSWG是确定和分析电网的安全需求，并开发出一套保证智能电网安全性和可靠性的危险应急预案。在这三个委员会和工作组的基础上，发展了6个DEWG和16个PAP。DEWG是对特定的应用领域进行研究，并进行分析和提供经验。PAP专注于目前已有标准的不足，以及一些亟待解决的问题。\r\n\r\n自动化学院在本次会议上参与的主要WG包括：\r\n\r\n1  PAP16风力发电通信\r\n\r\n主要关注风力发电设施在运行过程中需要传输的信息，包括：电压、电流、有功、无功、风速、转矩等。\r\n\r\n2  EMII WG\r\n\r\n主要关注电磁干扰问题，讨论如何增强智能电网设施的抗扰性能，判断电磁干扰源的类型是自然干扰还是人为干扰，判断电磁干扰途径是传导还是辐射等。由于关注问题的重要性SGIP大组讨论决定在下一次会议上成立PAP，专注讨论EMI问题。\r\n\r\n3  PAP12 & 13\r\n\r\n主要关注IEEE1815电力通讯分布式网络协议标注与IEC61850变电站通信网络与通信系统标准的关系，以及智能电网中应如何采用和发展标准。', 'The 2011 March 28 to 31 dr of automation of teachers in our school participated in winter nashvile meeting of the American standardization technical committee (NIST) smart grid interoperability platform (SGIP) standards work session. Our school were eight experts of automation in the standardization work SGIP working group. The group is in the American national strategic objectives should be about intelligent grid energy independence and security act (EISA) was established. The key is to study and work in the intelligent grid issued EISA related standard, information architecture and testing and certification system. Its aim is to build the advanced electric power system makes energy and information can be two-way interworking, and can ascend solar, wind and other renewable energy utilization. Its scope ranges from the family USES electricity to the transmission and substation, power distribution, then to power and energy storage and so on many electric fields.\r\n\r\nSGIP organizational structure, which is shown in the Governing Board, Officers and NIST SGIP SGIP managers, is responsible for the coordination and balance the relationship between technical field standard, and intelligent grid standards and the relationship between the traditional network standards. In the SGIP workgroup running processes, two standardization commission (SGAC and SGTCC) and a standardized working group (CSWG) is the core technical leadership. Among them are mainly discussed SGAC the smart grid a broad field, from technical Angle, application Angle and economic operation Angle subdivision into several branch area, with convenient various areas of the technical personnel discussion. SGTCC is discussed for each technical standard how to testing and certification. CSWG is to determine the safety requirements analysis and grid, and developed a set of guarantee the security and reliability of the intelligent grid risk emergency plan. In these three committee and working group, on the basis of the development DEWG and six 16 PAP. DEWG to specific application field is studied and analyzed and provide experience. PAP focus on existing standard is insufficient, and some issues that need to be resolved.\r\n\r\nIn this conference of automation of the main WG include: participation\r\n\r\n1 PAP16 wind power communication\r\n\r\nFocused on wind power facilities in the operation process of the information needs to be transmitted, including: voltage, current, active, reactive power, wind speed, torque, etc.\r\n\r\n2 EMII WG\r\n\r\nMain concern, electromagnetic interference to discuss how to strengthen intelligent power grid, the RNC resistance performance of the type of judge electromagnetic interference source is natural interference or human interference, judge electromagnetic interference way is conduction or radiation. Concerned about the importance of the problem of large groups, discuss the SGIP founded at the next meeting decision, focus discussion EMI problem of PAP.\r\n\r\n3 PAP12 & 13\r\n\r\nIEEE1815 focus mainly on electric power communication distributed network protocol with IEC61850 substation communication network marked with communication system standard relationship, and how should adopt in intelligent power grid and development of standard. ', '', '', '', '', 44),
(111, 1, '虚拟现实', 'Virtual Reality', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '　　VR是一项综合集成技术，涉及计算机图形学、人机交互技术、传感技术、人工智能等领域，它用计算机生成逼真的三维视、听、嗅觉等感觉，使人作为参与者通过适当装置，自然地对虚拟世界进行体验和交互作用。使用者进行位置移动时，电脑可以立即进行复杂的运算，将精确的3D世界影像传回产生临场感。该技术集成了计算机图形(CG)技术、计算机仿真技术、人工智能、传感技术、显示技术、网络并行处理等技术的最新发展成果，是一种由计算机技术辅助生成的高技术模拟系统。\r\n　　概括地说，虚拟现实是人们通过计算机对复杂数据进行可视化操作与交互的一种全新方式，与传统的人机界面以及流行的视窗操作相比，虚拟现实在技术思想上有了质的飞跃。\r\n　　虚拟现实中的“现实”是泛指在物理意义上或功能意义上存在于世界上的任何事物或环境，它可以是实际上可实现的，也可以是实际上难以实现的或根本无法实现的。而“虚拟”是指用计算机生成的意思。因此，虚拟现实是指用计算机生成的一种特殊环境，人可以通过使用各种特殊装置将自己“投射”到这个环境中，并操作、控制环境，实现特殊的目的，即人是这种环境的主宰。\r\n', 'VR is a comprehensive integration technology, involving computer graphics, human-machine interaction, sensing technology, artificial intelligence and other fields, it use computer to generate lifelike 3d sight and hearing and smell etc, make the person feels as participants through the appropriate devices, naturally on the virtual world experience and interaction. Users moves, the computer can position immediately complex operation, precise 3D world images back to produce telepresence. This technology has integrated computer graphics (CG) technology, computer simulation technology, artificial intelligence, sensing technology, display technology, network parallel-treatment technology achievements in the latest development, is a kind of generating by computer technology of high technology simulation system.\r\n\r\nGenerally speaking, the virtual reality is people through the computer for complex data visualization and interaction on a new way, and traditional human-machine-interfaces and popular Windows operating in technology, virtual reality than ideologically with a qualitative leap.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality "reality" is referring to in the physical sense or functional meaning world exists on any thing or environment, it can be actually achievable, also can be in fact elusive or cannot achieve. While "virtual" refers to use computer generated meaning. Therefore, the virtual reality is to use computer generated a special environment, people can use various special device will themselves "projection" to this environment, and operating, control environment and realizing specific purpose, namely person is the master of this kind of environment. ', '', '', '', '', 3),
(112, 1, '人工生命', 'Artificial life', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '　　虽然人工生命(AL)领域与人工智能(AI)领域的确有明显的重叠区,但他们有截然不同的初衷和演生史.以研究是否以及如何实现模拟智能的人工智能研究,早在计算机诞生后的初期就已经兴起,然而以试图澄清emergent behaviors的本质的人工生命的研究者们,可以说一直不知其他人在做类似的工作而孤军作战,直到80年代末,这个领域才正式的诞生。\r\n　　人工生命（artificial life）的概念，主要是指属于计算机科学领域的虚拟生命系统，涉及计算机软件工程与人工智能技术，人造生命是特指基因工程技术人工改造生物，90年代未中科院曾邦哲提出人工生物系统（artificial biosystem）的工程生物系统概念来整合计算机领域和遗传工程领域的两个概念，涉及合成生物学和系统生物工程技术。\r\n　　两种主导观念\r\n　　强人工生命:主张"生命系统的演化过程,是一个可以从任何特殊媒介物中抽象出来的过程."(John Von Neumann). Notably, Tom Ray 在Tierra模拟试验中第一次展示了,进化过程在有着抢占计算机存储空间之争的计算机程序的某种群体中极易发生。\r\n　　弱人工生命:认为通过不基于碳"生命过程"的生成是不可能的.他们的研究不是去模拟这一过程,而是试图去理解单个的现象。通常通过agent based model进行研究,它通常可提供最简的可能结论,就是: 我们不知道自然界中的什么生成了这种现象,但是通过模拟也许可以找到复杂生物现象的原理。', 'Although the artificial life (AL) fields and artificial intelligence (AI) fields have apparent overlap area, but they have distinct purpose and play. To study whether born history and how to simulate the intelligent artificial intelligence research, early in the early years of the computer after the birth, however, has developed to attempt to clarify the nature of emergent back the artificial life, say the researchers know others do similar has been in the job and alone, until the late 1980s, the birth of officially to this field.\r\n\r\nArtificial life (the concept of artificial act), is mainly refers to belong to the field of computer science, virtual life system involving computer software engineering and artificial intelligence technology, artificial life is referring to genetic engineering technology artificially transformation in the 1990s Chinese creatures, not CengBangZhe biological systems (artificial proposed artificially biosystem) engineering biological system conception to integrate computer field and genetic engineering field, involving the two concepts of synthetic biology and system biology engineering techniques.\r\n\r\nTwo dominant concept\r\n\r\nStrong artificial life: stands for "life system evolution, is a from any special medium can be abstracted process." (John Von Neumann). Notably, Tom Ray in Tierra simulated tests first shows, evolutionary process in have preempted computer storage space for certain groups of the computer program in easily happened. ', '', '', '', '', 5),
(113, 1, '虚拟现实的基本特征', 'The basic characteristics of virtual reality ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '多感知性（Multi-Sensory）\r\n　　所谓多感知是指除了一般计算机技术所具有的视觉感知之外，还有听觉感知、力觉感知、触觉感知、运动感知，甚至包括味觉感知、嗅觉感知等。理想的虚拟现实技术应该具有一切人所具有的感知功能。由于相关技术，特别是传感技术的限制，目前虚拟现实技术所具有的感知功能仅限于视觉、听觉、力觉、触觉、运动等几种。\r\n浸没感（Immersion）\r\n　　又称临场感，指用户感到作为主角存在于模拟环境中的真实程度。理想的模拟环境应该使用户难以分辨真假，使用户全身心地投入到计算机创建的三维虚拟环境中，该环境中的一切看上去是真的，听上去是真的，动起来是真的，甚至闻起来、尝起来等一切感觉都是真的，如同在现实世界中的感觉一样。\r\n交互性（Interactivity）\r\n　　指用户对模拟环境内物体的可操作程度和从环境得到反馈的自然程度（包括实时性）。例如，用户可以用手去直接抓取模拟环境中虚拟的物体，这时手有握着东西的感觉，并可以感觉物体的重量，视野中被抓的物体也能立刻随着手的移动而移动。\r\n构想性（Imagination）\r\n　　强调虚拟现实技术应具有广阔的可想像空间，可拓宽人类认知范围，不仅可再现真实存在的环境，也可以随意构想客观不存在的甚至是不可能发生的环境。\r\n　　由于浸没感、交互性和构想性三个特性的英文单词的第一个字母均为I，所以这三个特性又通常被统称为3I特性。\r\n　　一般来说，一个完整的虚拟现实系统由虚拟环境、以高性能计算机为核心的虚拟环境处理器、以头盔显示器为核心的视觉系统、以语音识别、声音合成与声音定位为核心的听觉系统、以方位跟踪器、数据手套和数据衣为主体的身体方位姿态跟踪设备，以及味觉、嗅觉、触觉与力觉反馈系统等功能单元构成。', 'Many receptivity (Multi - Sensory)\r\n\r\nSo-called refers to how perception in addition to giving a general computer technology has the visual perception, but also the auditory perception, force sleep perception, touch perception, motion perception, even including taste perception, olfactory perception, etc. The ideal virtual reality technology should have all has the perception function. Due to the related technologies, especially the sensing technology restriction, currently the virtual reality technology has the perception function is limited to visual, auditory, force sleep, touch, sports to wait for a few kinds.\r\n\r\nImmersion feeling (Immersion)\r\n\r\nAlso called telepresence, refers to the user feel as leading role exists in the true simulation environment level. The ideal simulation environment should users can scarcely tell true and false, and computer user to devote yourself to create 3-d virtual environment, the environment is really all the look, sounds really, moves is true, even smells, tastes and all feeling is really, as feeling like in the real world.\r\n\r\nInteractive (Interactivity)\r\n\r\nFor simulation environment that users can operate within the object the degree and get feedback from the environment of natural degree (including real-time). For example, the user can use a hand to grab the simulated environment directly in the object, then virtual hand is holding things feeling, and can feel the weight of the object in view of objects can also caught with hand moves immediately move.\r\n\r\nIdea sex (made)\r\n\r\nEmphasize the virtual reality technology should have broad can imagine space, can broaden the scope of human cognition, not only can reappear real environment, can also optional idea didn''t exist objectively even without possible environment.\r\n\r\nBecause submerged feeling, interactivity and idea of the English word of three characteristics of the first letters are I, so this three characteristics and is usually referred to as 3I characteristics.\r\n\r\nGenerally speaking, a complete virtual reality system, by virtual environment of high performance computer as the core of the virtual environment processors, with helmet displays for core visual system, to speech recognition, voice synthesis and sound localization is the core of the auditory system, Israel a tracker, data glove and data for the main body position clothing attitude tracking devices, and taste, smell, touch and force feedback system functional unit''s composition. ', '', '', '', '', 35),
(114, 10, '虚拟现实技术应用于心理治疗领域', 'Virtual reality technology applied in psychotherapy fields ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '心理治疗(psychotherapy)就广义而言,指任何对心理、情绪或行为障碍有减缓或治疗作用的技术和措施。1993年起,虚拟现实技术(以下简称VR技术)被应用于心理治疗领域。VR技术被定义为:“一种先进的人机界面,可以让使用者与计算机发生互动,并让使用者沉浸在计算机所创造的充满自然感受的人造环境中。”VR技术根据物理实现形式可分三种。(1)桌面式:用计算机显示器或其它台式显示器屏幕显示虚拟环境,该方法成本最低;(2)大屏幕式:即采用弧形宽屏幕、环形屏幕甚至全封闭的半球形屏幕,该方法视野大、使当事人和虚拟环境完全融合;虚拟效果接近完美,但成本相当高。(3)头盔式:是上述两种系统的折中,也是最常用的实现形式。利用头盔将观察对象拉近到当事人眼前,头盔上安装立体声系统和各种控制装置,将当事人同周围现实环境隔离[。1]组成头盔式VR系统,除了需要头盔式显示器,还需要一台用来创建互动三维视像的计算机和一副有触觉跟踪能力、可反馈使用者所处方位的数据手套。', 'Psychotherapy (psychotherapy) is broadly speaking, refers to any mental, emotional or behavioral problems have slowed or healing techniques and measures. Since 1993, the virtual reality technology (hereinafter referred to as the VR technology) is applied in the psychological therapy fields. VR technology is defined as: "an advanced man-machine interface, allowing users to interact with computers, and let users happened created enmeshed in computer with natural feeling of artificial environment." VR technology based on the physical realization forms can be divided into three kinds. (1) desktop type: using computer monitor or other desktop monitor screen virtual environment, this method lowest cost; (2) DaBing episodic: namely using arc wide-screen, circular screen even totally closed hemispherical screen, this method, so that the parties and range of virtual environment is fusion; Virtual effect, but near perfect quite expensive. (3) TouKuiShi: are these two systems of compromise, and most commonly used the realization form. Using the helmet will observe object to 104-102 before installation, the helmets stereo system and various control device, with around the realistic environment of isolation. 1] [TouKuiShi VR system, TouKuiShi display, besides need used to create interaction still need a 3d video computer and a pair of have a sense of touch tracking ability, can feedback user a data glove prescription. ', '../pic/2011052347207_XLKX200803.jpg', '虚拟现实技术应用于心理治疗领域', '', '', 12),
(115, 30, '虚拟伊拉克帮助士兵克服创伤应激障碍', 'Virtual Iraq help the soldiers to overcome trauma stress disorder ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '创伤后应激障碍（PTSD）新的研究显示，通过虚拟现实暴露疗法对从阿富汗和伊拉克返回的士兵的进行康复性治疗对患者非常有效。经过短短七个疗程日，士兵反映，他们的创伤后应激障碍症状正在减少，并且近三分之二士兵表示治疗所产生的变化是可靠的和有意义的。\r\n\r\n     暴露疗法的设想是在安全的环境让具有创伤后应激障碍（PTSD）的人重温他们的痛苦经历。在过去，传统方式是治疗师帮助士兵回想他们的痛苦的回忆，并要求他们想象当时场景和声音。虚拟现实暴露疗法（VRET）在这个基础之上，进一步通过虚拟现实技术，根据实际情况模拟出的各种需要的场景和声音。\r\n\r\n     这项技术是由国防部远距离保健科学技术中心联合心理健康防御中心以及位于马迪根的创伤性脑损伤与心理学系为期4年的研究的一部分。 VRET是根据陆军作战经验，采用360度的交互式计算机生成的虚拟系统，运行的程序称为“虚拟伊拉克”。病人戴上头盔显示器，而医生负责编排有关的场景因素，直升机、枪声、甚至穆斯林式的祈祷。一个典型的治疗过程会持续90分钟。\r\n\r\n     VRET（Virtual reality exposure therapy）并不新近出现的，在对越南退伍军人和在世界贸易中心911恐怖袭击的幸存者的治疗中已经被证明是有效的。根据有关报告，最早的应用至少可追溯到1999年。但最近几年才把这项研究研究扩展为现役大部分军人。\r\n\r\n     格雷格·雷杰（Greg   Reger）博士是该项研究领导人，他认为，由于这一代的士兵是在高科技的环境长的，“虚拟现实”的概念对他们非常有吸引力。雷杰（Reger）在新闻发布会上说：“这可能是虚拟现实暴露疗法(VRET)会提供一个更有吸引力，让那些年轻的，精精通技术入伍，并让退伍军人继续服务。此外，这种治疗方法可以让被治疗者减少“耻辱感”，因为传统治疗方法相比，那些可能因为战场上恐惧退缩的士兵可以通过远程访问进入VRET，不必向治疗师亲自描述战场上的尴尬情况。换句话说，者避免了那些可能“临阵退缩”军人的尴尬，让他们仿佛进入一个很酷的视频游戏。\r\n\r\n     另一方面，虚拟现实技术还可以帮助训练治疗师。两年后，南加州大学社会工作学院开始使用一个患有创伤后应激障碍士兵的虚拟化身，帮助训练军队中那些偶尔可能被新的病人吓到的治疗师。', 'Post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD), new research shows through the virtual reality exposure therapy from Afghanistan and Iraq returns to the soldier''s rehabilitation sex therapy is very effective for patients. After just seven treatment, soldiers, they reflect on the post-traumatic stress disorder symptoms is declining, and nearly two-thirds the soldiers say the change is generated by the treatment of reliable and meaningful.\r\n\r\nThe idea of exposure therapy is in a safe environment that is post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) to renew their sufferings. In the past, the traditional way is to therapists to help soldiers recall their painful memories, and asking them to imagine that scene and sound. Virtual reality exposure therapy (VRET) in this foundation, further through the virtual reality technology, according to the actual situation of the various needs simulates the scene and the voice.\r\n\r\nThe technology is by defense distance health sciences, technology center jointly mental health defense centers and is located in the MaDiGen traumatic brain injury and the psychology department of the four years of the study. VRET is according to the army combat experience, adopt the 360 interactive computer-generated virtual system, operation of the procedure called "virtual Iraq". The patient wears a helmet display, but the doctor responsible for layout related scene factors, helicopters, gunfire, even the prayers of Muslim type. A typical treatment process will continue to 90 minutes.\r\n\r\nVRET exposure therapy) order reality doesn''t appear recently, on the Vietnam veterans and on the world trade center terrorist attack survivors of treatment has proven to be effective. According to the report, the application of the earliest dates back at least 1999. But in recent years to get the study research expanded to active duty most soldiers.\r\n\r\nGreg reggie Greg dr Reger) (is the study leader, he thinks, because this generation of soldiers in the high-tech environment long, "virtual reality" concept for they are very attractive. Reggie (Reger) said at a news conference: "this may is virtual reality exposure therapy (VRET) will provide a more attractive, let those young, pure technical proficiency, and let the army veterans continue service. In addition, this treatment can let be healers reduce" ChiRuGan ", because the traditional treatment compared to those may because battlefield shrinking soldiers can through fear VRET, remote access into don''t have to describe the battlefield of the therapist personally embarrassing situation. In other words, those who might opt to avoid the "withdrawal" soldiers awkward, let them as if into a cool video games.\r\n\r\nOn the other hand, the virtual reality technology can also help training therapists. Two years later, the university of southern California institute of social work began using a post-traumatic stress disorder soldiers virtual incarnation, helping to train troops who occasionally may be in new patients to frighten therapist. ', '../pic/2011052397593_050812171631890.jpg', '虚拟伊拉克帮助士兵克服创伤应激障碍', '', '', 39),
(117, 20, '翟振明教授', 'Zhenming', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '　　翟振明教授，1957年12月生。1982年7月毕业于北京钢铁学院，获工科学士学位；1984年考取中山大学哲学系硕士研究生，于1986年赴美留学，并开始兼职任教。1993年5月获美国University of Kentucky 哲学博士学位，同年8月至2000年5月，先后在Millsaps College、Muhlenberg College、Moravian College 任教。2000年7月开始，出任中山大学哲学系教授、博士生导师。\r\n　　在美国的14年期间，翟教授从学术训练上打下了欧洲大陆哲学和英美分析哲学的基础，在此基础上探讨人类生活各方面涉及的先验依据。他治学的特点是原创性和系统性，不拘泥于传统的哲学内部的学科分界。他最早关注的是伦理道德判断的形上学，并围绕这个主题写下了第一本专著。近年来，他集中思考的是与"虚拟实在"有关的形而上学问题。在他的第二本专著中，翟教授用思想实验、逻辑分析和现象学方法论证了自然实在与虚拟实在的极端形式之间的三种虚实判断的对称性，认为自然实在的"背后"不比虚拟实在有更多的本体论承托。\r\n', 'ZhaiZhenMing professor, born in December 1957. In July 1982 graduated from Beijing steel institute, won the engineering bachelor''s degree; In 1984, sun yat-sen university graduate department admitted, in 1986, and began to teach abroad part-time. In May 1993 Kentucky leads by the United States of a Ph.D. In the same year, August to May 2000, successively in Millsaps college.i, Muhlenberg college.i Moravian college.i teaching,. Beginning in July 2000, sun yat-sen university professor of philosophy as, doctoral tutor.\r\n\r\nIn the United States during the 14 years, torres from academic training professor on the European continent philosophy and laid the foundation of Anglo-American analytical philosophy, on the basis of exploring human all aspects of life involves a priori basis. His research is characteristic of originality and systemic, not constrained the philosophy of subject boundary inside. He is the first concern is the metaphysics of the ethical and moral judgment around this topic, and wrote the first book monographs. In recent years, he focused his thinking is with "virtual reality" the relation of metaphysical questions. In his second books, torres by thought experiment, professor of logical analysis and phenomenological method demonstrates with virtual reality of natural really extreme forms of three judge between unionizing the symmetry, the "truly think natural behind" unlike virtual reality more ontology supporting. ', '../pic/2011052379645__20090826090845_MS0y.jpg', '翟振明教授', 'Zhenming Zhai', '', 27);
