(118, 20, '陈清奎教授', 'QingKui Chen', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '陈清奎，山东建筑大学教授、虚拟现实实验室主任，曾境策划（香港）控股集团虚拟现实研发中心首席专家。兼任济南动漫游戏协会理事，上海世博会山东馆主题创作团队专家、网上世博山东馆专家。多年从事CAD/CAM/CAE及虚拟现实技术研究开发工作，完成多项科研项目，主编出版教材6本，发表论文20余篇，获国家专利5项。 2005年获第九届“挑战杯”山东省大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛优秀指导教师奖。先后主持开发完成了国家863计划CIMS应用示范工程--山东常林集团CHL-CIMS应用示范工程，CAD/CAM及CIMS技术研究与应用示范（山东省科技厅项目），主持开发了建筑楼盘虚拟现实展示系统、旅游景点虚拟现实展示系统、产品网络在线虚拟展示系统、公交资讯导航系统、数字城市技术、动漫和虚拟重大应急预案综合平台、塔式起重机虚拟培训系统、三维立体投影展示系统开发等重大项目的应用软件系统开发。', 'ChenQingKui, shandong construction university professors, virtual reality lab director, once borders planning (Hong Kong) holding group virtual reality r&d center chief expert. Concurrently jinan animation games association, member of Shanghai world expo shandong museum theme creation team experts, online expo shandong museum experts. Years of experience in CAD/CAM/CAE and virtual reality technology research and development work, complete several research projects, edited and published materials published six, the paper 20, five of national patents. 2005 attains the 9th "challenge cup" shandong university student extracurricular academic science and technology works excellent teachers award competition. He has successively presided development completed state 863 plan CIMS application demonstration project CHL - ChangLin group - shandong CIMS application demonstration project, CAD/CAM and CIMS technology research and application demonstration (shandong department project), presided over the construction of virtual reality development dish tourist attractions display system, virtual reality display system, product online virtual display system, bus information navigation systems, digital city technology, animation and virtual major emergency plan comprehensive platform, tower crane virtual training system, 3d projection display system development and other important projects in the software system development. ', '../pic/2011052367854_1178847264669.jpeg', '陈清奎教授', 'QingKui Chen', '', 21),
(119, 30, '数字油田信息化管理系统', 'Digital oilfield information management system ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '  随着社会全面发展和社会主义市场经济的高速发展，安全生产问题已经成为社会各界的关注焦点，这一问题过去一直以来的高投入，效率低的方式如今显然已经无法走通，然而如何才能真正做到投入与效果的平衡甚至是低投入、高效率。利用虚拟现实技术构建油田安全作业虚拟仿真训练系统，提供多人在线交互式训练功能，进而推行封闭式演示、指南式向导操作以及开放式自由操作等培训模式可以很好的解决这一问题。因此开发油田安全作业虚拟仿真训练系统已经势在必行，中海油率先行动，与北京中天灏景网络科技有限公司共同实施，推出了《中海油××油田设备管理系统》。\r\n\r\n    北京中天灏景率先提出了基于Web浏览器的分布式三维生产辅助决策系统的概念，并将此概念应用于多个项目的实施，均取得了良好的效果。此次的三维辅助决策系统集生产管理、设备管理、应急推演等功能于一体并结合网络通信技术、数据库技术形成一个行之有效的综合性系统，为客户带来了极大的便利与价值。', 'Along with the social development and the socialist market economy, the high-speed development of production safety problem has become the focus of the society focus, the problem in the past have been high investment, low efficiency way now have apparently can''t walk through, but how to truly input and effect of the balance is even lower investment, high efficiency. Using virtual reality technology build oilfield safety training simulation system, provide virtual multiplayer online interactive training function, thus pushing closed-end demonstration, guide type operation and open free operation guide such training model can well solve the problem. Therefore oilfield development virtual simulation training system safe operations, it is first action with Beijing, China national offshore oil corporation (cnooc Hao zhongtian landscape network technology Co., LTD. Jointly implementation, launched the cnooc x oilfield equipment management system ".\r\n\r\nBeijing zhongtian Hao scene first put forward the distributed based on Web browser 3d produce auxiliary decision system, and the concept of this concept applied to multiple project implementation, all achieved good effect. The 3d aided decision-making system integrating production management, equipment management, emergency derivation and combining functions in one network communication technology, database technology form an effective comprehensive system for our clients, brought great convenience and value. ', '../pic/2011052338742_pingtai4.jpg', '数字油田信息化管理系统', 'Digital oilfield information management system ', '', 14),
(120, 50, '2008中国虚拟现实', '2008 China virtual reality ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '培训时间：2008年07月25日(10:00-17:00)\r\n培训地点：北京DRC工业设计创意产业基地 培训教室\r\n　　　　（北京市西城区新街口外大街28号DRC基地一层）\r\n培训人数：50人\r\n　　虚拟现实技术，被誉为21世纪最神奇的计算机图形图像技术，也是未来CG产业的发展趋势之一，近年来已经获得了日益广阔的应用：建筑设计、城市规划、地产、家装设计、工业仿真、教学科研、文物复原等行业，它越来越多的出现在人们的视野中。为了更好的促进中国虚拟现实行业的发展，为广大用户提供强大的虚拟现实制作工具，我们特举办此次中国虚拟现实（VR-Platform）免费培训讲座（第22期）。\r\n　　VR-Platform是中国第一款成功发布的虚拟现实制作软件， 在国内具有最高的成熟度和普及率，它的出现，让虚拟现实产业从高端走向低端，从神坛走向平民。 目前，已经有数以万计的学员参加过培训，成为中国虚拟现实行业的中坚力量！我们欢迎更多的用户和爱好者前来参加！\r\n	\r\n1.VRP奠基人，技术总监：王老师\r\n2.业界资深培训讲师：陈老师\r\n3.虚拟现实引擎开发专家：李老师\r\n4.资深VR培训讲师：柳老师\r\n \r\n1.此次培训侧重于虚拟现实技术在工业设计领域内的应用,了解最前沿的虚拟现　实发展动态，如web3d技术、多通道环　幕展示技术、物理引擎技术等\r\n2.掌握虚拟现实项目的制作流程，以及能够实现的技术功能\r\n3.虚拟现实精彩案例：某国家级重点项目制作过程讲解\r\n4.登高望远，提前了解未来行业需求，为今后的发展打下基础\r\n5.与业内专业人士进行沟通交流，结识更多合作伙伴。', 'Training time: the 2008 07 January 25 (10:00 - from 17:00)\r\n\r\nTraining site: Beijing DRC industrial design originality industry base training classrooms\r\n\r\n(Beijing xicheng district XinJieKou DRC base outside street 28 a layer)\r\n\r\nTraining toll: 50 people\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology, known as the 21st century the most magical computer image technology, and also the development trend of future CG industry in recent years, has been one of the obtained increasingly wide applications: architectural design, the urban planning, real estate, domestic outfit design, industrial simulation, and teaching and research, cultural relic recovery industries, it more and more appear in people''s horizon. In order to promote the development of China''s virtual reality industry, providing our customers with powerful virtual reality production tools, we hereby to hold the Chinese virtual reality (VR - Platform) free training seminars (22nd stage).\r\n\r\nVR - Platform is China first paragraph release virtual reality making success in domestic software, have the highest maturity and popularity, its occurrence, let the virtual reality industries from high-end to low-end, from shrines to civilians. At present, has tens of thousands of students attended training, becoming China''s virtual reality industry backbone power! We welcome more users and lovers to participate!\r\n\r\n1. VRP founder, technical director: wang\r\n\r\n2. Industry senior training instructors: Chen\r\n\r\n3. Virtual reality engine development experts: miss li\r\n\r\n4. Senior VR training instructors: miss liu\r\n\r\n1. The training focused on virtual reality in the field of industrial design application, understanding to the forefront of virtual reality now, such as web3d technology development tendency, multichannel ring screen display technology, physics engine technology, etc\r\n\r\n2. Master of virtual reality project process, and can realize technical functions\r\n\r\n3. Virtual reality wonderful case: a national key project production process to explain\r\n\r\n4. Climb up a distant view, the sooner the future industry needs for future development, lay the foundation\r\n\r\n5. With industry professionals for communication, to make more partners. ', '', '2008中国虚拟现实', '2008 China virtual reality ', '', 7),
(121, 50, '虚拟现实设计师免费培训讲座4月18日', 'Virtual reality stylist free training lectures April 18th ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '本次讲座内容\r\n1．此次培训侧重于虚拟现实技术在虚拟教学、多媒体技术、专业应用、虚拟实训、虚拟现实课件制作等领域内的应用，了解最前沿的虚拟现实发展动态，如web3d技术、多通道环幕技术、物理引擎技术等。\r\n2．掌握虚拟现实项目的制作流程，以及能够实现的技术功能\r\n3．虚拟现实精彩案例：某国家级重点项目制作过程讲解\r\n4．登高望远，提前了解未来行业需求，为今后的发展打下基础\r\n5．与业内专业人士进行沟通交流，结识更多合作伙伴。\r\n \r\n本次讲座对象\r\n1．  建筑设计、城市规划、土木工程\r\n2．工业仿真、机械设计、产品制造\r\n3．数字媒体、动漫、游戏\r\n4．水利水电、电力、矿井、油田\r\n5．艺术设计、服装设计\r\n6．旅游、园林、景观\r\n7．交通、道路桥梁\r\n8．文物古迹、人文复原\r\n9．军事模拟\r\n10．对虚拟现实技术感兴趣的其他人员等\r\n \r\n本次培训受益：\r\n1、  了解最新虚拟现实行业发展动态及行业应用前景；\r\n2、  能够开拓新视野，发现新项目，虚拟现实属于朝阳行业，投资少，回报高；\r\n3、  了解虚拟现实制作流程；\r\n4、  登高望远，提前掌握未来行业需求，为今后的发展打下基础\r\n与业内专业人士进行沟通交流，结识更多合作伙伴。', 'The lecture content\r\n\r\n1. The training focused on virtual reality technology in virtual teaching, multimedia technology, professional application, virtual training courseware, virtual reality in fields of the application of virtual reality, understanding the forefront of dynamic, such as web3d technology development, multi-channel HuanMu technology, physics engine technology, etc.\r\n\r\n2. Master of virtual reality project process, and can realize technical functions\r\n\r\n3. Virtual reality wonderful case: a national key project production process to explain\r\n\r\n4. Climb up a distant view, the sooner the future industry needs for future development, lay the foundation\r\n\r\n5. With industry professionals for communication, to make more partners.\r\n\r\nThe lecture object\r\n\r\n1. Architectural design, the urban planning, the civil engineering\r\n\r\n2. Industrial simulation, mechanical design, product manufacturing\r\n\r\n3. Digital media, comic, game\r\n\r\n4. Water conservancy and hydropower, electric power, oil field, mine\r\n\r\n5. Art design, fashion design\r\n\r\n6. Tourism, architecture, landscape\r\n\r\n7. Traffic, roads and Bridges\r\n\r\n8. Cultural relics, humanity recover\r\n\r\n9. Military simulation ', '', '', '', '', 6),
(122, 50, '信息学院虚拟现实VR—Platform培训系列讲座', 'Virtual reality VR - information institute Platform training lecture series', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '2010年4月14日下午1：30，信息学院在2号楼五层机房成功举办了第一场虚拟现实VR—Platform培训讲座，讲座人为中视典数字科技有限公司的郭老师。\r\n\r\n上学期，信息学院在2号楼五层机房建立了一个3dSMax&虚拟现实工作室，里面有相关的一系列配套设备，还有超大银幕、观赏沙发等。该新项目受到学院领导的支持与重视，旨在让信息学院的学生在课余时间学习到前沿的技术，亲自体验与制作虚拟现实场景，为以后就业奠定更广阔的知识基础。\r\n\r\n本学期，在信息学院王学军老师、申蔚老师的带领下，学院与中视典数字科技有线公司开展合作，举办虚拟现实VR—Platform培训系列讲座。同学们对虚拟现实技术表现出极大的兴趣与热情，虽然当天机房座位有限，但是很多同学都搬椅子前去听课，机房内座无虚席。本次培训首先对虚拟现实技术概况、虚拟现实使用范围、VRP软件做了相应的介绍，并展示了一系列经典案例，如：某小区景观虚拟现实，紫禁城虚拟现实等。随后介绍了VRP软件安装及插件配置，并以简单空间几何体为例进行了软件使用的入门教学。休息期间，王老师向同学们开放了工作室，同学们戴上专用观赏眼镜通过大银幕观看虚拟现实经典作品，亲身感受了虚拟现实的神奇与魅力。\r\n\r\n此次培训结束之际，申蔚老师表达了对同学们的期望与鼓励，希望同学们能珍惜这宝贵的机会，通过坚持参加虚拟现实VR—Platform培训系列讲座并结合自己认真学习，相信将来同学们一定可以很好地掌握虚拟现实技术，最终将有机会进入相关领域公司实习与工作。\r\n\r\n ', 'April 14, 2010 at 1:30 p.m., tower 2 information institute five floors successfully hosted the first game engine room virtual reality VR - Platform training seminars, lectures artificial CTV Canon digital technology Co., LTD. Guo teacher.\r\n\r\nLast semester, tower 2 information institute five floors in the engine room built a studio 3dSMax & virtual reality, there are a series of related equipment and large screen, watch the sofa. This new project led by college support and attention of information institute, aiming to make the students'' interest in learning to leading edge technology time, personally experience and making virtual reality scene, for later obtain employment laid more broad knowledge foundation.\r\n\r\nThis semester, in WangXueJun teacher, information institute ShenWei the guidance of teachers, college and CTV Canon digital technology cooperation, cable companies hold virtual reality VR - Platform training lecture series. The students on virtual reality technology showed great interest and enthusiasm, although the day room seats are limited, but many students to move the chair lecture, the telecom room full of people. This training first of virtual reality technology situation, virtual reality use scope, VRP software made the corresponding introduction, and display a series of classic case, such as: some small area landscape virtual reality, the Forbidden City virtual reality, etc. Then introduces VRP software installation and plug-in with simple configuration and space for an example of geometry to use of introductory teaching software. Rest period, teacher wang to classmates open studios, the classmates wear special viewing glasses watch virtual reality by the big screen classic works of virtual reality, experience the magic and glamour.\r\n\r\nAt the end of the training, ShenWei teachers expressed their classmates about expectations and encouragement, we hope our students can cherish this precious opportunity to attend virtual reality VR - Platform training lecture series and combining study hard carefully, believe the future students can grasp well the virtual reality technology, eventually will have the opportunity to enter the relevant field company internship and job. ', '', '', '', '', 10),
(123, 50, '百所院校VR技术讲座', '100 schools VR technology lectures ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '讲座信息\r\n巡讲时间：2010年5月-2010年12月\r\n讲座地点：全国各大院校\r\n主办单位：中视典数字科技有限公司\r\n授课对象：专业老师、学生\r\n授课形式：免费\r\n公司网址：http://www.vrp3d.com/\r\n讲座合作单位\r\n·中国图像图形学学会\r\n·北京工业设计促进中心\r\n·教育部虚拟现实应用工程研究中心\r\n中视典数字科技，是专注于虚拟现实与仿真领域的软硬件研发与推广的专业机构， 是国际领先的虚拟现实技术解决方案供应商和相关服务提供商，我们提供的产品包括：\r\n·虚拟现实编辑器（VRP-BUILDER）\r\n·数字城市仿真平台（VRP-DIGICITY）\r\n·物理模拟系统（VRP-PHYSICS）\r\n·三维网络平台（VRPIE）\r\n·工业仿真平台（VRP-INDUSIM）\r\n·虚拟旅游平台（VRP-TRAVEL）\r\n·网络三维虚拟展馆（VRP—MUSEUM）\r\n·三维仿真系统开发包（VRP-SDK）\r\n·多通道环幕立体投影解决方案\r\n\r\n中视典于2002年注册于深圳高新技术园区，之后分别在北京、上海、成都设立了分支机构。中视典VRP系列产品子问世以来，一举打破该领域被国外软件所垄断的局面，以极高的性价比获得国内广大客户的喜爱，已成为目前国内市场占有率最高的一款国产虚拟现实平台软件。已有超过300所院校采购了VRP虚拟现实平台及其相关硬件产品（如清华大学电机系、上海同济大学建筑学院、中国传媒大学动画学院、天津大学水利工程学院、青海海洋学院、武汉理工大学、山东理工大学、澳门科技大学、北京建筑工程学院、石家庄信息工程职业学院、广西机电职业技术学院、武汉商业服务学校、无锡旅游商贸职业学校等），在院校的教学和科研中发挥了重要的作用。\r\n', 'Lecture information\r\n\r\nCruise speak time: 2010 May - December 2010\r\n\r\nThe venue: national universities and colleges\r\n\r\nOrganizer: CTV Canon digital technology Co., LTD\r\n\r\nTeaching object: professional teachers, students\r\n\r\nTeaching form: free\r\n\r\nThe company website: http://www.vrp3d.com/\r\n\r\nLecture the cooperation unit\r\n\r\n· China image graphics to learn\r\n\r\n· Beijing industrial design promotion center\r\n\r\nVirtual reality application engineering, the ministry of education research center\r\n\r\nCTV Canon digital technology, is focused on virtual reality and simulation areas of software and hardware development and promotion of professional institutions, is the international leading virtual reality technology solution provider and related services provider, we provide products including:\r\n\r\n· virtual reality editor (VRP - BUILDER)\r\n\r\n· digital city simulation platform (VRP - DIGICITY)\r\n\r\n· physical simulation system (VRP - PHYSICS)\r\n\r\n· three-dimensional network platform (VRPIE)\r\n\r\n· industrial simulation platform (VRP - INDUSIM)\r\n\r\n· virtual tour platform (VRP - my)\r\n\r\n· network 3d virtual hall (VRP - MUSEUM)\r\n\r\n3d simulation system, setups (VRP - SDK)\r\n\r\n· multi-channel HuanMu stereo projection solutions\r\n\r\nCTV festival in 2002 registered in shenzhen hi-tech park, after in Beijing, Shanghai, respectively set up the branch office in chengdu. CTV Canon VRP series product since the advent, overtaking the son break the field were foreign software monopoly situation, with extremely high cost-effective access to domestic customers love, has become the current domestic market share of the highest one paragraph domestic virtual reality platform software. More than 300 schools purchasing a VRP virtual reality platform and related hardware products (such as tsinghua university electrical engineering department, Shanghai tongji university architecture college, animation school, communication university of China hydraulic engineering institute, tianjin university Marine institute, qinghai province wuhan university of technology, shandong polytechnic university, macau university of science and technology, Beijing institute of civil engineering and architecture, shijiazhuang information engineering vocational college, guangxi electromechanical vocational and technical college, wuhan commercial service schools, wuxi travel and trade vocational school, etc.), the teaching and scientific research in college plays an important role. ', '', '', '', '', 8),
(124, 10, '人工生命研究的新进展', 'New development of artificial life ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '自从1987年兰顿提出人工生命的概念以来，人工生命研究已走过了13年的历程。人工生命的独立研究领域的地位已被国际学术界所承认。在1994年创刊并在世界著名学府麻省理工学院出版的国际刊物《人工生命》（Artificial Life），是该研究领域内的权威刊物。网络上的人工生命资源非常丰富，人工生命的网上园地Zooland曾在《科学》杂志上得到专门的报道。\r\n\r\n到目前为止，人工生命学术界举办了7次里程碑式的国际学术会议，这几次人工生命会议构成了该学科发展轨迹在时间维上的重要坐标点。\r\n\r\n人工生命的这7次学术会议简要评述如下：\r\n\r\n   （1）“人工生命——关于生命系统合成与模拟的跨学科研讨会”。本次会议于1987年9月在美国新墨西哥的罗斯阿拉莫斯举行。这次会议一般被简称为“A LIFEⅠ”。本次会议的论文集共收录了24篇论文，内容主要分布在：人工生命研究的理论、生命现象的仿真、细胞自动机（简称CA）、遗传算法、进化仿真等5个方面，兰顿发表了题为“人工生命”的开拓性论文，他在文中提出了人工生命的概念，并讨论了它作为一门新兴的研究领域或学科存在的意义。兰顿被公认为人工生命研究的创立者。这次会议标志着人工生命研究领域的诞生。\r\n\r\n（2）“人工生命Ⅱ——人工生命研讨会”。本次会议于1990年2月在美国新墨西哥的圣菲举行），简称ALIFEⅡ。该会议论文集共收录了31篇论文，内容分为概貌、自组织、进化动力学、开发、学习与进化、计算、哲学与突现、未来等8部分。其中兰顿的“混沌边缘的生命”、约翰·科赞（John Koza）的“遗传进化和计算机程序的共进化”属于经典之作。\r\n\r\n（3）“人工生命Ⅲ——人工生命研讨会”，1992年6月在美国新墨西哥的圣菲举行，简称为ALIFE Ⅲ。本次会议的论文集共收录了26篇论文，内容除涉及遗传算法、进化仿真、突现行为、适应度概貌图、群体动力学和混沌机制等人工生命经典内容之外，还讨论了机器人规划应用问题。科赞的“人工生命：自我复制的自发突现与进化的自改进计算机程序”堪称杰作，从遗传编程算法方面探讨了在人工生命研究中关键的突现机理。\r\n\r\n   （4）“人工生命IV——第四届国际生命系统合成与模拟研讨会”，1994年7月在美国麻省理工学院举行，简称为ALIFE IV。本次会议的论文集共收录了56篇论文，内容分为特邀报告、长文和短文3个部分，它覆盖了协同进化、遗传算子、进化与其它方法（如神经网络等）的综合、AL算法、关于混沌边缘和分岔的研究、AL建模、学习能力、进化动力学、细胞自动机、DNA非均衡学说研究、人工生命在字符识别、机器人等方面的应用等较为广泛的内容。\r\n\r\n（5）“人工生命Ⅴ——第五届国际生命系统合成与模拟研讨会”，1996年5月16-18，在日本古城奈良举行，来自世界各地的500多名学者参加了会议。这是人工生命首次在亚洲召开的国际会议。人工生命概念刚提出，就引起日本学者的关注，第一次人工生命国际会议就有日本学者参加。这次会议在日本的召开，标志着日本成为亚洲人工生命研究的中心。\r\n\r\n（6）“人工生命VI——第六届国际人工生命研讨会”，1998年6月26-29在美国洛杉矶加利福尼亚大学举行。这次会议的主题是“生命和计算：变化着的边界”。本次会议收到大约100篇提交的论文，其中39篇作为完整论文在这次会议的论文集中得到介绍。有9篇论文被认为是人工生命的新的高质量工作。这次会议主要的论文涉及的是计算的分子和细胞生物学。会议提供了许多新的关于发育过程、细胞分化机理和免疫反应模型制造的新见解。这些论文把人工生命扩展到令人兴奋的新方向。\r\n\r\n(7)“人工生命Ⅶ——回顾过去，展望未来”, 于2000年8月1-6日在美国波特兰的里德学院举行。本次会议的主题是：“回顾过去，展望未来”。具体讨论的问题有以下几个方面：生命的起源、自组织和自复制问题，包括人工化学进化、自催化系统、虚拟新陈代谢等；发育和分化问题，包括人工的和自然的形态发生，多细胞分化与生物进化，基因调节网络等；进化和适应动力学问题，包括人工进化生态学，可进化性及其对生物组织的影响，进化计算等；机器人和智能主体，包括进化机器人，自主适应机器人和软件智能体等；通讯、协作和集体行为，包括突现集体行为，通讯和协作的进化，语言系统、社会系统、经济系统和社会-技术系统等；人工生命技术和方法的应用，包括工业和商业的应用，可进化硬件、自修复硬件和分子计算，金融和经济学，计算机游戏，医疗应用，教育应用等；认识论和方法论基础问题，包括人工生命的本体论、认识论以及伦理和社会影响等。\r\n\r\n除了这些会议之外，一些地区性的国际会议也不断地被组织。“欧洲人工生命会议”（European Conference on Artificial Life，简称ECAL）已连续举办5次会议，每次会议都有论文集出版。ECAL是国际人工生命研究的一个重要论坛。\r\n\r\n人工生命被认为是走向21世纪的科学。兰顿的老师法默在题为“人工生命：即将来临的进化”的演讲中曾这样说到：“随着人工生命的出现，我们也许会成为第一个能够创造我们自己后代的生物”，“作为创造者，我们的失败会诞生冷漠无情、充满敌意的生物，而我们的成功则会创造风采夺人、智慧非凡的生物。这种生物的知识和智慧将远远超过我们。当未来具有意识的生命回顾这个时代时，我们最瞩目的成就很可能不在于我们本身，而在于我们创造的生命。人工生命是我们人类潜在的最美好的创造。”[6]当然，许多人可能不像法默这么乐观，但人工生命在21世纪肯定会有重大的突破则是毫无疑问的。', 'Abram since 1987''s concept of proposed artificial life, artificial life since has passed 13 years of history. Artificial life independent research field position has been international academic circles admitted. Founded in 1994, in this world-renowned MIT press international publication artificially of Life (Artificial act), is the study domain authoritative publication. The artificial life on the network resources are very rich, artificial life Zooland was in the online garden science magazine. A special report\r\n\r\nSo far, artificial life academia held seven times landmark international academic conferences, this meeting several times artificial life constitute the development track of this subject in the temporal dimension on important points.\r\n\r\nThe seven times the artificial life briefly described as follows: conference\r\n\r\n(1) "artificial life - about life system synthesis and simulation of interdisciplinary workshop". The meeting in 1987 in the United States in September, new Mexico''s Ross held ramos. This meeting is generally referred to as "A act Ⅰ". The proceedings of the meeting were recorded 24 papers, content is mainly distributed in the theory of life research: the artificial simulation, of the phenomena of life and cellular automata (hereinafter referred to as CA), genetic algorithm, evolution simulation from five aspects, such as Syria''s entitled "artificial life published a paper, he" pioneering in this paper proposes the concept of artificial life, and discuss it as a new field of study or discipline the meaning of existence. LAN meal is acknowledged as the founder of artificial life research. The conference marked the birth of research in the field of artificial life.\r\n\r\n(2) "artificial life Ⅱ -- artificial life seminar". The meeting in February 1990 in new Mexico''s Santa fe, referred to Ⅱ ALIFE held). This conference proceedings were recorded 31 papers, content is divided into general view, self-organizing, evolutionary dynamics, development, to learn and evolve, calculation, philosophy and emergence, eight parts. Future One LAN''s "edge of chaos" life "and John secco Koza) praise (John" genetic evolution and computer program altogether evolution "belongs to the classic.\r\n\r\n(3) "artificial life -- artificial life Ⅲ conference, June 1992 new Mexico in the United States held Santa fe, referred to as Ⅲ ALIFE. The proceedings of the meeting were recorded content 26 papers, involving genetic algorithm, except evolution simulation, emergence behavior, fitness mannagemant figure, group dynamics and chaotic mechanism artificial life beyond classical content, but also discuss the robot planning application problems. Secco praise "artificial life: self-replicating spontaneous emergence and evolution since improve computer program" count masterpiece, from genetic programming algorithm in artificial life is discussed key emergent mechanism research.\r\n\r\n(4) "artificial life IV - the fourth international life system synthesis and simulation conference in July 1994, held at the Massachusetts institute of technology, referred to as ALIFE IV. The proceedings of the meeting were recorded for 56 papers, content is divided into invited report, deregulation plan and the short three parts, it covers co-evolutionary, genetic operator, evolution and other methods (such as neural networks etc) comprehensive, AL algorithm, the edge of chaos and bifurcation about the research, AL modeling, ability to learn, evolutionary dynamics, theory of cellular automata, DNA research, artificial life disequilibrium in character recognition, the robot, the application of a wide range of content such as.\r\n\r\n(5) "artificial life Ⅴ - the fifth international life system synthesis and simulation seminar", in May 1996 16 to 18, held in Japan, nara city from all over the world more than 500 academics attended the meeting. This is the first artificial life of an international conference in Asia. Artificial life concept first put forward, cause the attention of Japanese scholars, the first international conference of artificial life have Japanese scholars participate. The meeting held in Japan, marking Japan to become Asia research center of artificial life.\r\n\r\n(6) "artificial life VI - the sixth international symposium" artificial life, June 1998 26-29 in university of California, Los Angeles, USA held. The purpose of this meeting is to "life and calculation: changing boundary". The conference had about 100 essays submitted papers, including 39 articles in this meeting as a complete paper are introduced the thesis focus. Nine papers was considered artificial life new high quality work. This meeting is related to the main papers calculation of molecular and cellular biology. Meeting provides many new about development process, cell differentiation mechanism and immune response model manufacture new insights. These papers to artificially life extension to exciting new direction.\r\n\r\n(7) "artificial life Ⅶ -- looking back on the past, looking to the future", in August 2000 1-6 of reed college in the United States held in Portland. The conference theme is "looking back on the past, looking to the future". The problems discussed in the following aspects: the origin of life, self-organization, and since copy problems, including artificially chemical evolution, autocatalytic system, virtual metabolism, etc.; Growth and differentiation question, including artificial and natural form happen, many cell differentiation and biological evolution, gene regulatory network, etc.; Evolution and adapt dynamics problems, including artificially evolutionary ecology, evolution of sexual and the influence of biological tissue, evolutionary computation, etc.; Robots and agents, including evolution robot, autonomous robots and software to agents, etc.; Communication, coordination and collective behavior, including dash forward show collective action, communication and cooperation of evolution, language system, social system, economic system and social - technology systems; Artificial life technologies and methods of applications, including industrial and commercial applications, evolvable hardware, self-repairing hardware and molecular computing, finance and economics, computer games, medical applications, education application, etc; Epistemology and methodology of artificial life based issues, including the ontology, epistemology and ethics and social influence.\r\n\r\nIn addition to these meetings, some regional outside the international conference also are constantly organization. "The European Artificial Life meeting on European Artificial" (as markets, it hasn''t been made clear already continuously held ECAL) five meetings, each meeting proceedings are published. International ECAL is one of the important research artificial life BBS.\r\n\r\nArtificial life towards the 21st century was considered the science. Syria in farmer''s teacher entitled "artificial life: upcoming evolution" speech had said: "with the emergence of artificial life, we may become the first to create our own offspring of biological", "as a creator, our failure be born indifference, hostile creatures, not our success will create elegant demeanour seize person, wisdom, extraordinary creatures. This creature of knowledge and wisdom will far exceed our conscious. When the future life, when we review the age the most outstanding achievement is not our probably itself, but rather we create life. Artificial life is our human potential best creation." [6] and, of course, many people may not like farmer so optimistic, but in the 21st century of artificial life will certainly have significant breakthrough is of no doubt. ', '', '', '', '', 25),
(125, 30, '数字城市规划平台模块', 'Digital urban planning platform module ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '1.虚拟城市规划，仿真城市风貌\r\n    利用虚拟现实技术、地理信息技术、数据压缩技术、网络技术等各种高科技手段，模拟出一个全三维、逼真的城市环境，建立城市规划、建设和运营管理的三维空间信息系统，提高城市规划管理水平，保障建设项目与城市环境的协调发展。\r\n\r\n2.辅助规划审批，规避投资风险\r\n    为建设工程审批提供决策依据，保障城市规划管理工作的科学性。通过对建立的虚拟城市环境中地物的编辑，直观反映报审建设项目与其周边城市现状环境之间的空间关系，辅助规划审批。提高建设工程报审效率，规避建设投资风险。突破传统建设项目报审制作平面效果图及三维动画的技术模式，节约传统技术模式下修改方案及表现手段需要的大量时间，缩短城市建设项目审批周期，在一定程度上规避城市建设的投资风险。\r\n\r\n3.辅助城市土地与房产管理\r\n    利用强大的数据库支持，系统可以很方便的实现信息的查询、检索。可以快速显示并且按比例缩放建模区域的数字图形、建筑物实际影像，并可根据单位名称、公安门牌在场景中进行快速定位，也能通过与房产管理局产权属与交易办公自动化系统链接，根据图纸内容快速定位于相对应的房产权属属性记录、房产平面图或分层分户图，或者根据产权登记记录快速定位到三维场景中的建筑。\r\n4.宏观调控城市区域经济结构\r\n    VRP-DIGICITY 数字城市仿真平台可以对城市建筑、园林绿化、道路桥梁、电缆管线、排污管道、商业区、高新区、居民区、高校区等各种区块进行实时分层显示和管理，从不同角度观察城市规划的布局和结构，动态研究城市规划中的空间体系、轮廓线以及位置关系。而且这些数据资料还可以和建筑容积率等指标建立动态连接，从而实现城市设计数据和三维空间形象的一致性。\r\n\r\n5.建立信息平台，服务城市建设\r\n    建立城市空间信息平台，为三维数字地图奠定基础，为城市发展提供信息服务，可通过互联网发布三维数字地图，为社会各界提供城市控件信息服务。\r\n城市规划不仅仅是规划单位的事情，决策者、相关部门以及公众都在城市设计和实际建设中扮演不通的角色，有效的展示规划信息可以提供更加准确的决策和公平的参与。充分的沟通是保证城市设计最终成功的前提，而VRP-DIGICITY为这种沟通提供了一个理想的平台。\r\n\r\n6.展示规划成果，加强公共参与\r\n    VRP-DIGICITY数字城市演示系统可以让观看者无需复杂的学习，即可实现各种方式的交互浏览，让观看者生动感受城市规划的成果。用户可以任意设定观察角度，运动速度和运动路径，实现游戏般的漫游，非常直观和生动，是展示和汇报城市规划成果的最佳方式。', '1. A virtual city planning, simulation of urban style\r\n\r\nUsing the virtual reality technology, geographic information technology, data compression technology, network technology, etc. Various kinds of high-tech means, simulate a full 3d, lifelike urban environment, establishing the city planning, construction and operation management of 3d information system, improve the urban planning and management level, ensuring the construction projects and the coordinated development of the urban environment.\r\n\r\n2. Auxiliary planning approval, avoiding investment risk\r\n\r\nFor construction project examination and approval, ensure provide decision-making basis for urban planning management work scientific. Through a virtual city environment of the editor, intuitive features in its BaoShen construction projects reflect the surrounding city status quo environment space between the relationship, auxiliary planning for examination and approval. Improve construction project, to evade construction investment BaoShen efficiency risks. Break the traditional construction project BaoShen making plane rendering 3d animation technology mode and the traditional technology, saving under the mode of modification plan and performance means need lots of time, shorten the cycle of urban construction project examination and approval, and, to some extent, avoid city construction investment risk.\r\n\r\n3. Auxiliary urban land and property management\r\n\r\nUsing powerful database support, the system can easily achieve information query, retrieval. Can quickly display and scaling modeling of digital graphics, building area, and but according to actual image addresses unit name, public security in the scene, also can rapid positioning with real estate administration property of office automation system with trade links, according to drawings content fast locate in corresponding property ownership property records, housing plan or stratified according to individual figure, or quick location to the property right registration records of the buildings of 3d scene.\r\n\r\n4. Macro-control urban regional economic structure\r\n\r\nVRP - DIGICITY digital city simulation platform for urban construction, can landscaping, roads and Bridges, cable line, sewage pipes, commercial, high-tech zone, residential areas, and various blocks university district real-time layered display and management, from different angles of the layout and structure of the urban planning, the dynamic research city planning in the space system, contour line and the position relations. And these data can also and building volume index build dynamic connection, so as to realize the urban design data and 3d image consistency.\r\n\r\n5. Establishing the information platform, service the urban construction\r\n\r\nEstablish urban spatial information platform, and lay the foundation for the three-dimensional digital map for urban development, provide information through Internet service issued three-dimensional digital map, to the community, to provide urban control information services.\r\n\r\nUrban planning is not only planning unit thing, decision makers, relevant departments and the public in urban design and practical construction, plays the role of impassability show planning information can effectively provide more accurate decision-making and fair to participate. Sufficient communication is the guarantee urban design ultimately successful premise, and for this communication DIGICITY VRP - provides an ideal platform.\r\n\r\n6. Displaying planning achievements, strengthen the public participation\r\n\r\nVRP - DIGICITY digital city demonstration system can let viewers without complex study, can realize the interaction in various ways to browse, let the viewer vivid experience urban planning results. Users can set arbitrary view, sports speed and movement path, realize the game of roaming, very intuitive and vivid, report is to show and the best way to urban planning achievements. ', '', '', '', '', 23),
(126, 30, '环幕投影VR实验室', 'Screen projection VR laboratory ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '    多通道环幕（立体）投影系统是指采用多台投影机组合而成的多通道大屏幕展示系统，它比普通的标准投影系统具备更大的显示尺寸、更宽的视野、更多的显示内容、更高的显示分辨率，以及更具冲击力和沉浸感的视觉效果。该系统可以应用于教学、视频播放、电影播放（现在好多影视院采用这种方式）等。\r\n\r\n    多通道环幕（立体）投影系统由于其技术含量高、价格昂贵，以前一般用于虚拟仿真、系统控制和科学研究，近来开始向科博馆、展览展示、工业设计、教育培训、会议中心等专业领域发展。其中，院校和科博馆是该技术的最大应用场所。这种全新的视觉展示技术更能彰显科博馆的先进性和创新性，在今后若干年内不会被淘汰。 \r\n\r\n    中视典数字科技，凭借其强有力的软件研发能力和硬件系统集成能力，一直致力于多通道环幕（立体）投影系统的开发与研究，已经为国内多个院校和科博馆及相关单位建设了多套环幕投影系统，其技术的先进性在业内具有很高的声誉，并屡次打破国内多通道数量记录（分别是南京城规馆 7 通道和大连北良 10 通道）。目前，中视典数字科技已经成为国内环幕系统集成的领军企业之一。 \r\n\r\n    我们服务的重点客户包括：南京城规规划展览馆 300 度 7 通道环幕系统、上海张江科技园 4 通道环幕立体展示系统、大连北良港 10 通道背投展示系统、武汉理工大学3通道环幕立体展示系统、天津大学 3 通道环幕立体投影系统、华北水电仿真实验室、萧山城市规划展览馆 3 通道环幕系统、北京师范大学双通道立体投影系统、北京交通大学多通道系统等。', 'Multichannel HuanMu (3d) projection system is refers to using multiple projector with a combination of multi-channel big screen display system, it than ordinary standard projection system has greater display size, wider vision, more show content, the higher the display resolution, and more powerful and immersed sense of visual effect. This system can be applied to teaching, video playback, movie play (now a lot of film and television courtyard that way), etc.\r\n\r\nMultichannel HuanMu (3d) projection system due to its high technical content, expensive, commonly before virtual simulation, system control for and scientific research recently began to kebo hall, exhibition, industrial design, education training, conference center and other professional field. Among them, colleges and kebo gallery is the technology''s biggest application places. This brand-new visual display technology can reveal the more advanced and innovative fair museum, in the next several years will not be eliminated.\r\n\r\nCTV Canon digital technology, with its powerful software research and development ability and hardware system integration ability, has been committed to the multichannel HuanMu (stereo) projection system development and research, has many universities and colleges and for domestic and relevant unit construction fair museum has many sets of HuanMu projection system, its technical sophistication in the industry have a very high reputation, and often break domestic multi-channel quantity records (NaJingCheng rules were passageway and hall 7 dalian beiliang 10 channel). At present, CTV Canon digital technology has already become the domestic HuanMu system integration is one of leading enterprise.\r\n\r\nWe service clients include: the key NaJingCheng gage planning exhibition hall is 300 degrees 7-channel HuanMu system, Shanghai zhangjiang science park 4 channel HuanMu stereo display system, dalian north harbor 10 channel DLP projection display system, wuhan university of technology HuanMu stereo display system three channels the three channels, tianjin university HuanMu 3d projection system, north hydroelectric simulation lab, xiaoshan urban planning exhibition hall three channels HuanMu system, Beijing normal university, dual channel 3d projection system of Beijing jiaotong university multi-channel system, etc. ', '', '', '', '', 12);
INSERT INTO `20article` (`id`, `itm_id`, `title_chs`, `title_eng`, `username`, `date`, `content_chs`, `content_eng`, `pic`, `picdesc_chs`, `picdesc_eng`, `fileupload`, `click_throughs`) VALUES
(127, 50, '信息传播学院举行虚拟现实与数字艺术专题讲座', 'Information dissemination institute of virtual reality and digital art held seminars ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '2011年4月22日下午，我院云龙报告厅座无虚席，爱迪斯通（北京）科技有限公司华东地区总经理李協顺、江苏地区业务经理李弘毅先生为我们带来了题为“虚拟现实与数字艺术”的精彩讲座。本次讲座由刘行芳副院长主持，数字媒体艺术、广告学、数字艺术设计（美术学院）等专业的任课教师、本科生和部分研究生近400人聆听了讲座。\r\n\r\n李協顺经理从3D/VR虚拟现实、技术应用案例、虚拟现实的系统环境等几个方面做了精彩介绍。他幽默风趣的话语和精彩生动的演示，给同学们带来一份听觉和视觉上的盛宴，赢得了同学们的阵阵掌声。李弘毅先生从市场转型谈起，从技术角度出发，给同学们详细讲解了“Shiva 3D的编辑环境”、“编辑器工作流程”、“发布流程”，让同学们进一步的了解了这门新技术，拓展了同学们的视野。他最后通过实际操作，用“虚拟试车”、“乐高玩具”、“鬼娃娃”等一个个生动有趣的例子,展示了“D''fusion虚拟现实”的具体应用，引起同学们极大兴趣。交流环节，同学们从如何学习和掌握这门技术等方面，向李弘毅先生请教。他毫无保留地解答了同学们的疑惑，使在场同学深受启发。\r\n\r\n最后，刘院长代表我院师生对爱迪斯通公司两位主讲人表达了诚挚谢意。他指出，当今是新媒体时代，新媒体环境的核心是技术，作为新时代的同学们应该努力学习、刻苦钻研，掌握新技术，提高专业技能。', 'The 2011 April 22 afternoon, our full yunlong lecture hall, Eddie stone (Beijing) technology Co., LTD LiXie along the east China area general manager, jiangsu area sales manager for we brought Mr LiHongYi entitled "virtual reality and digital art" excellent lecture. The lecture LiuHangFang hosted by vice President, digital media art, advertising, digital art design (academy of fine arts), and other professional teachers, undergraduate and postgraduate nearly 400 people listen to part of the lecture.\r\n\r\nLiXie shun manager from 3D/VR virtual reality, technology application cases, virtual reality system environment and so on several aspects made wonderful introduction. His humorous words and colorful show, give schoolmates to bring a hearing and visual regale, win the students burst of applause. Mr. LiHongYi from market transition from technology mentioned, Angle, to the classmates explains editor of Shiva 3D "environment", "editor work flow", "release process", let classmates further understanding of the new technology, expand the horizons of students. He finally through the actual operation, use "virtual commissioning", "lego toys" and "ghost doll" wait for each vivid and interesting example, demonstrates "D ''fusion virtual reality" specific application, cause the classmates great interest. The exchange, students from how to learn and master the skill to Mr LiHongYi aspects, ask. He spoke without reserve answer the students doubt inspired, presence classmate.\r\n\r\nFinally, LiuYuanChang represents our teachers and students of Ed stone company two keynote speakers expressed sincere gratitude. He pointed out that, nowadays is the new media era, new media environment that is the core of technology, as the new times students should study hard, study assiduously, mastering new technologies, improve their professional skills. ', '', '', '', '', 9),
(128, 50, '虚拟现实及研究最新进展、动漫游戏和多媒体对联', 'Virtual reality and research the latest progress, anime game and multimedia couplet ', 'admin', '2011-05-23', '题目⑴: 虚拟现实及研究最新进展（2：30-3：40）\r\n \r\n题目⑵：动漫游戏和多媒体对联（3：50-5：00）\r\n \r\n时间：2009年4月27日（周一）下午2：30\r\n \r\n地点：数理信息学院一楼报告厅\r\n\r\n个人简介：\r\n        潘志庚 研究员是浙江大学计算机应用重点学科虚拟现实与网络多媒体方向的主要带头人, 博士生导师。目前的主要研究方向为：虚拟现实、数字娱乐与游戏、多媒体计算等。潘志庚研究员与国内外多家单位开展广泛的学术交流，有多次组织国际学术会议的成功经验，并承担欧盟科技项目，应邀担任欧盟科技项目评审专家。发表国际期刊论文60多篇, SCI/EI论文40/70篇; 获得2008年国家科技进步二等奖, 2001年教育部科技进步二等奖. 2003-2005任浙江省特聘教授(钱江学者), 2006-2008任南京师范大学讲座教授. \r\n      主要学术兼职包括：中国图像图形学会常务理事，中国图像图形学会虚拟现实专委会主任; 国际期刊IJVR主编, 国际期刊TRANSACTIONS ON EDUTAINMENT副主编,国际期刊 International Journal of Image and Graphics （IJIG）编委；国际期刊 International Journal of CAD/CAM 编委；欧盟框架六计划项目评议专家[2003-2006]；国际信息联合会（IFIP）娱乐计算工作委员会中国代表。', 'Topic: (1) : virtual reality and research the latest progress (2.30 - then the)\r\n\r\nTopic (2) : anime game and multimedia couplet (3:50-5:00)\r\n\r\nTime: April 27, 2009 2:30 p.m. (Monday)\r\n\r\nLocation: mathematical information institute, the first floor lecture hall\r\n\r\nProfile:\r\n\r\nPanZhiGeng researcher is zhejiang university computer application key discipline virtual reality and network multimedia direction of the main leaders, doctoral supervisor. The present main research direction for: virtual reality, digital entertainment and games, multimedia calculations, etc. PanZhiGeng researcher and the domestic and foreign many units carried out extensive academic exchanges, have to organize many successful experience of international academic conferences, and assume the eu technology project, he was invited to be the eu science and technology project evaluation experts. International journal articles published more than 60 papers, SCI/EI papers 40/70 article; Get the 2008 national science and technology progress prize of ministry of education, science and technology progress prize in 2001. 2003 to 2005 as zhejiang qianjiang scholars professor (soe), 2006-2008 as chair professor of nanjing normal university.\r\n\r\nThe main academic part-time include China society of image and graphics, standing director of China society of image and graphics, director of virtual reality branch; International Journal editor, IJVR TRANSACTIONS ON International journals EDUTAINMENT deputy editor, International Journal of International plos IJIG) and add a little (vice-editor; International Journal of International plos CAD/CAM editors; The eu framework six project evaluation experts [2003-2006]; International information federation (IFIP) entertainment computing working committee the representative of China. ', '', '', '', '', 9),
(130, 60, '虚拟现实技术的国内外研究现状', 'Virtual reality technology research situation ', 'admin', '2011-05-24', '　　摘要：虚拟现实技术是一门新兴边缘的技术，研究内容涉及多个领域，应用十分广泛，被公认为是21世纪重要的 发展 学科以及影响人们生活的重要技术之一。从虚拟现实的概念出发，对虚拟现实技术的国内外研究现状进行了充分论述，并展望了虚拟现实的发展趋势。\r\n　　关键词：虚拟现实；研究现况；发展趋势\r\n　　中图分类号：F061.3　 文献 标识码：A　文章编号：1672-3198(2009)02-0279-02 中国论文联盟www.LWLM.com编辑。\r\n　　\r\n　　1　虚拟现实\r\n　　\r\n　　虚拟现实(Virtual Reality，简称VR)，又译为临境，灵境等。从应用上看它是一种综合 计算 机图形技术、多媒体技术、人机交互技术、 网络 技术、立体显示技术及仿真技术等多种 科学 技术综合发展起来的计算机领域的最新技术，也是力学、数学、光学、机构运动学等各种学科的综合应用。这种计算机领域最新技术的特点在于以模仿的方式为用户创造一种虚拟的环境，通过视、听、触等感知行为使得用户产生一种沉浸于虚拟环境的感觉，并与虚拟环境相互作用从而引起虚拟环境的实时变化。现在与虚拟现实有关的内容已经扩大到与之相关的许多方面，如“人工现实”(Artifi- cial Reality)、“遥在”(Telepresence)、“虚拟环境”(Virtual Environment)、“赛博空间”(Cyberspace)等等。\r\n　　\r\n　　2　国外虚拟现实技术研究现状\r\n　　\r\n　　计算机的发展提供了一种计算工具和分析工具，并因此导致了许多解决问题的新方法的产生。虚拟现实技术的产生与发展也同样如此，概括的国内外虚拟现实技术，它主要涉及到三个研究领域：通过计算图形方式建立实时的三维视觉效果；建立对虚拟世界的观察界面；使用虚拟现实技术加强诸如科学计算技术等方面的应用。\r\n　　\r\n　　2.1　VR技术在美国的研究现状\r\n　　美国是虚拟现实技术研究的发源地，虚拟现实技术可以追溯到上世纪40年代。最初的研究应用主要集中在美国军方对飞行驾驶员与宇航员的模拟训练。然而，随着冷战后美国军费的削减，这些技术逐步转为民用，目前美国在该领域的基础研究主要集中在感知、用户界面、后台软件和硬件四个方面。\r\n　　上世纪80年代，美国宇航局(NASA)及美国国防部组织了一系列有关虚拟现实技术的研究，并取得了令人瞩目的研究成果，美国宇航局Ames实验室致力于一个叫“虚拟行星探索”(VPE)的实验计划。现NASA已经建立了航空、卫星维护VR训练系统，空间站VR训练系统，并已经建立了可供全国使用的VR 教育 系统。北卡罗来纳大学的计算机系是进行VR研究最早最著名的大学。他们主要研究分子建模、航空驾驶、外科手术仿真、建筑仿真等。乔治梅森大学研制出一套在动态虚拟环境中的流体实时仿真系统。施乐公司研究中心在VR领域主要从事利用VRT建立未来办公室的研究，并努力设计一项基于VR使得数据存取更容易的窗口系统。波音公司的波音777运输机采用全无纸化设计，利用所开发的虚拟现实系统将虚拟环境叠加于真实环境之上，把虚拟的模板显示在正在加工的工件上，工人根据此模板控制待加工尺寸，从而简化加工过程。\r\n　　图形图像处理技术和传感器技术是以上VR项目的主要技术。就目前看，空间的动态性和时间的实时性是这项技术的最主要焦点。\r\n　　\r\n　　2.2　VR技术在欧洲的研究现状\r\n　　在欧洲，英国在VR开发的某些方面，特别是在分布并行处理、辅助设备(包括触觉反馈)设计和应用研究方面。在欧洲来说是领先的。英国Bristol公司发现，VR应用的交点应集中在整体综合技术上，他们在软件和硬件的某些领域处于领先地位。英国ARRL公司关于远地呈现的研究实验，主要包括VR重构问题。他们的产品还包括建筑和科学可视化计算。\r\n　　欧洲其它一些较发达的国家如：荷兰、德国、瑞典等也积极进行了VR的研究与应用。\r\n　　瑞典的DIVE分布式虚拟交互环境，是一个基于Unix的，不同节点上的多个进程可以在同一世界中工作的异质分布式系统。\r\n　　荷兰海牙TNO研究所的物理 电子 实验室(TNO- PEL)开发的训练和模拟系统，通过改进人机界面来改善现有模拟系统，以使用户完全介入模拟环境。\r\n　　德国在VR的应用方面取得了出乎意料的成果。在改造传统产业方面，一是用于产品设计、降低成本，避免新产品开发的风险；二是产品演示，吸引客户争取定单；三是用于培训，在新生产设备投入使用前用虚拟工厂来提高工人的操作水平。\r\n　　2008年10月27-29日在法国举行的ACM Symposi- um on Virtual Reality Software and Technoogy大会，整体上促进了虚拟现实技术的深入发展。', 'Abstract: virtual reality technology is a new branch of edge technology, the research content, involving multiple fields used widely, is recognized as the development of the 21st century is an important subject and influence people living important technical one. Starting from the concept of virtual reality of virtual reality technology, the research situation paper discussed sufficiently, and prospects the development trend of virtual reality.\r\n\r\nKeywords: virtual reality; Research status; Development trend\r\n\r\nChinese F061.3 literature classification number: mark code: A articles Numbers: 1672-3198 (2009) 02-0279-02 Chinese paper alliance. www.LWLM.com editor\r\n\r\n1 virtual reality\r\n\r\nVirtual Reality (VR), the abbreviation insgroupsto Reality, and translated into the environment, such as lingjinghutong. Look from the application of it is a kind of integrated computation machine graphics technology, multimedia technology, man-machine interactive technology, network technology, three-dimensional display technology and simulation technology and so on many kinds of science and technology of comprehensive development up to the latest technology of the computer field, but also mechanics, mathematics, optics, kinematics comprehensive application of various disciplines. The field of computer latest technology features to mimic the way for users to create a virtual environment, through the sight and hearing and touch perception behavior allows the user to produce such a immersed in a virtual environment, and the feeling of interaction with the virtual environment caused the real-time virtual environment changes. Now with the Virtual Reality related content has expanded to many aspects of the related, such as "artificially Reality" (Artifi - cial Reality), "remote Telepresence), in" (" Virtual Environment "(to)," order "(cyber space beloved" angel), etc.\r\n\r\n2 foreign virtual reality technology research situation\r\n\r\nThe development of the computer provides a computing tools and analytical tools, and thus led to many new methods of solving problems of produce. Virtual reality technology production and the development also so, summary of virtual reality technology at home and abroad, it mainly involves three research field: through calculation and graphics ways to create real-time three-dimensional visual effect; Based on the virtual world observation interface; Using virtual reality technology to strengthen such as scientific computing technology application.\r\n\r\nIn the United States 210 VR technology research status\r\n\r\nThe United States is the birthplace of virtual reality technology research, virtual reality technology dates back to the 1940s. The first study mainly concentrated in the U.S. military applied to the simulation with astronaut flyboy by training. However, as the cold war, the United States military cuts after these technologies to civilian use gradually for the U.S. in the fields of basic research mainly concentrated in perception, the user interface, the backend software and hardware four aspects.\r\n\r\nThe 1980s, NASA and U.S. defense department organized a series about virtual reality technology research, and achieved remarkable results, NASA Ames laboratory working on a planetary exploration called "virtual" (VPE) experiment plan. Now NASA has established airlines, satellite maintenance VR training system, the space station, and has been training system of VR established for the national education system using VR. Computer science at the university of north Carolina is the most famous research vr-cnc college. They mainly study molecular modeling, aviation driving, surgical simulation, building simulation, etc. George mason university developed a set of virtual environment in the fluid dynamic real-time simulation system. Xerox research center in VR field using VRT mainly engaged in the research, establish the future office and trying to design a based on VR allows data access easier to window system. Boeing transport adopted the Boeing 777 paperless design, use development of the virtual reality system will virtual environment on the real environment, superimposed on the virtual template displayed in the workpiece is processed according to this template control, workers, which can simplify for finishing size process.\r\n\r\nImage processing technology and sensor technology is above the main technology project VR. Now look, space and the time of the dynamic real-time is this technology most main focus.\r\n\r\n2.2 VR technique research status in Europe\r\n\r\nIn Europe, the UK in VR development, especially in certain aspects of distributed parallel processing, auxiliary equipment (including tactile feedback) design and application. It is leading in Europe. UK Bristol company found intersections, VR applications should be focused on comprehensive technology, they are some of the areas in the software and hardware are in a leading position. British ARRL company to present research about far experimental, mainly including VR reconstruction. Their products include building and scientific visualization calculation.\r\n\r\nOther European more developed countries like the Netherlands, Germany, Sweden the VR is also actively research and application.\r\n\r\nSweden''s ever distributed virtual interaction environment based on Unix, is a different nodes of multiple processes can work in the same world of heterogeneous distributed system.\r\n\r\nThe Netherlands institute of TNO physical electrical laboratory (TNO - the PEL) training and simulation system developed by improved human-computer interface to improve existing simulation system, giving users a completely intervention to simulate the environment.\r\n\r\nThe application of German in VR made unexpected results. In transform traditional industries, one is used for product design, reduce cost, avoid the risk of new product development; 2 it is product demonstrations, attract clients for order; Three is used for training, in the new production equipment input with virtual factory before using the operating level to improve workers.\r\n\r\n27 October 2008-29 in France Symposi - um at ACM Technoogy insgroupsto Reality Software and on the whole assembly, promote the development of Virtual Reality technology. ', '../pic/2011052450012_ba191ad141d047feafdd569764498374.jpg', '虚拟现实技术的国内外研究现状', 'Virtual reality technology research situation ', '', 12),
(131, 60, '综述虚拟现实技术及其应用', 'Virtual reality technology and its application were reviewed ', 'admin', '2011-05-24', '摘要：虚拟现实技术是二十世纪末才兴起的一门崭新的综合性信息技术，在最近几年发展迅速，其应用领域设计到教育、军事、娱乐和医学等许多行业。本文概述了虚拟现实技术的概念、基本特征和技术分类，提出了虚拟现实技术发展的技术瓶颈，阐述了虚拟现实技术应用和优势。\r\n关键词：虚拟现实；沉浸；交互；想象；\r\nVirtualReality；Immersion；Interaction；Imagination\r\n虚拟现实技术的概念\r\n虚拟现实技术是一项综合集成技术，它的出现是计算机图形学、人机交互技术、传感器技术、人机接口技术以及人工智能技术等交叉与综合的结果。它利用计算机生成逼真的三维视觉、听觉、嗅觉等各种感觉，使用户通过适当装置，自然地对虚拟现实世界进行体验和交互作用。简单地说，虚拟现实技术就是用计算机创造现实世界。\r\n虚拟现实技术特征\r\n1993年BurdeaG在Electro93国际会议上发表的“VirtualRealitySystemandApplication”一文中，提出了虚拟现实技术三个特征，即：沉浸感、交互性、想象性。\r\n沉浸感是指用户可以沉浸于计算机生成的虚拟环境中和使用户投入到计算机生成的虚拟场景中的能力，用户在虚拟场景中有“身历其境”之感。它所看到的、听到的、嗅到的、触摸到的，完全与真实环境中感受的一样。它是虚拟现实系统的核心。\r\n交互性是指用户与虚拟场景中各种对象相互作用的能力。它是人机和谐的关键性因素。用户进入虚拟环境后，通过多种传感器与多维化信息的环境发生交互作用，用户可以进行必要的操作，虚拟环境中做出的相应响应，亦与真实的一样，如拿起虚拟环境中的一个篮球，你可以感受到球的重量，扔在地上还可以弹跳。交互性包含对象的可操作程度及用户从环境中得到反馈的自然程度、虚拟场景中对象依据物理学定律运动的程度等，例如，当物体受到力的作用时，物体会沿着力的方向移动、翻到或者从桌面落到地面等。\r\n想象性是指通过用户沉浸在“真实的”虚拟环境中，与虚拟环境进行了各种交互作用，从定性和定量综合集成的环境中得到感性和理性的熟悉，从而可以深化概念，萌发新意，产生熟悉上的飞跃。因此，虚拟现实不仅仅是一个用户与终端的接口，而且可以使用户沉浸于此环境中获取新的知识，提高感性和理性熟悉，从而产生新的构思。这种构思结果输入到系统中去，系统会将处理后的状态实时显示或由传感装置反馈给用户。如此反复，这是一个学习——创造——再学习——再创造的过程，因而可以说，虚拟现实是启发人的创造性思维的活动。\r\n虚拟现实技术的分类\r\n虚拟现实是从英文VirtualReality一词翻译过来的，Virtual就是虚假的意思，Reality就是真实的意思，合并起来就是虚拟现实，也就是说本来没有的事物和环境，通过各种技术虚拟出来，让你感觉到就如真实的一样。\r\n实际应用的虚拟现实系统可分为四类：\r\n一、桌面虚拟现实系统，也称窗口中的虚拟现实。它可以通过桌上型机实现，所以成本较低，功能也最简单，主要用于CAD、CAM、建筑设计、桌面游戏等领域。\r\n二、沉浸虚拟现实系统，如各种用途的体验器，使人有身临其境的感觉，各种培训、演示以及高级游戏等用途均可用这种系统。\r\n三、分布式虚拟现实系统，它在因特网环境下，充分利用分布于各地的资源，协同开发各种虚拟现实的利用。它通常是浸沉虚拟现实系统的发展，也就是把分布于不同地方的沉浸虚拟现实系统，通过因特网连接起来，共同实现某种用途。美国大型军用交互仿真系统NPSNet以及因特网上多人游戏MUD便是这类系统。\r\n四、增强现实又称混合现实系统。它是把真实环境和虚拟环境结合起来的一种系统，既可减少构成复杂真实环境的开销，又可对实际物体进行操作，真正达到了亦真亦幻的境界，是今后发展的方向。\r\n虚拟现实技术发展的瓶颈\r\n虚拟现实技术的发展过程中碰到的问题很多，可以归结为3大难题：\r\n4．1虚拟现实设备的“贵族化”。要构建一个高质量的虚拟现实系统，首先需要昂贵的外部设备，无论是高分辩率的头盔显示器HMD，还是立体投影显示器，无论是空间定位器，还是高精度的数据手套，都是价格不菲。其次，为完成复杂场景的实时渲染，还需要高性能的图形工作站以及相应的软件。在一些专用领域，但普通的信息系统用户可能会望而却步。\r\n4．2繁琐的三维建模。基于图形的虚拟环境首先要解决的问题便是三维造型。当图形渲染技术在向实现真实感大踏步前进的时候，生成精确三维模型的过程还像二十几年前一样困难。在三维激光扫描技术上的进步提供了简化模型构造过程的一些承诺。然而，这些自动化模型获取方法也验证了真实世界的几何是极端复杂的。大部分的模型仍需要人工绘制，而且需要聘请高水平的专业人士，所以其费用是相当惊人的。比如在电影《坦克尼克号》中，为实现场景三维建模及各种特技处理所花的人工费用高达2500万美元，这笔钱足以制造一艘同样规模的真船。繁琐的三维建模也是制约虚拟现实技术发展的严重障碍。\r\n4．3数据量大。虚拟现实技术要想得到很大的发展，需要与Internet结合，这恐怕已是不争的事实。目前虚拟现实技术应用的数据量仍然很大，在现有网络整体速度较慢的情况下，Internet用户必须等待较长时间，这往往令人难以忍受。我们应该在虚拟现实系统中考虑数据压缩问题，这个问题可能现在还未引起人们的重视，但是随着应用的深入，这是一个不可回避的问题。\r\n虚拟现实技术的应用前景和优势\r\n虚拟现实技术的应用极为广泛，Helsel与Doherty在1993年对全世界范围内已经进行的805项虚拟现实研究项目作了统计，结果表明：目前在娱乐、教育及艺术方面的应用占据主流，其次是军事与航空，医学，商业，另外在可视化计算、制造业等方面也有相当的比重。下面简要介绍其部分应用。\r\n\r\n\r\n医学虚拟现实技术应用大致上有两类。一是虚拟人体，也就是数字化人体，这样的人体模型医生更轻易了解人体的构造和功能。另一是虚拟手术系统，可用于指导手术的进行。\r\nPieper及Satara等研究者在90年代初基于两个SGI工作站建立了一个虚拟外科手术练习器，用于腿部及腹部外科手术模拟。这个虚拟的环境包括虚拟的手术台与手术灯，虚拟的外科工具，虚拟的人体模型与器官等。借助于HMD及感觉手套，使用者可以对虚拟的人体模型进行手术。但该系统有待进一步改进，如需提高环境的真实感，增加网络功能，使其能同时培训多个使用者，或可在外地专家的指导下工作等。\r\n娱乐、艺术与教育丰富的感觉能力与3D显示环境使得虚拟现实技术成为理想的视频游戏工具。由于在娱乐方面对虚拟现实的真实感要求不是太高，故近些年来虚拟现实技术在该方面发展最为迅猛。如Chicago开放了世界上第一台大型可供多人使用的虚拟现实娱乐系统，其主题是关于3025年的一场未来战争；英国开发的称为“Virtuality”的虚拟现实游戏系统，配有HMD，大大增强了真实感；1992年的一台称为“LegealQust”的系统由于增加了人工智能功能，使计算机具备了自学习功能，大大增强了趣味性及难度，使该系统获该年度虚拟现实产品奖；\r\n军事与航天工业模拟与练一直是军事与航天工业中的一个重要课题，这为虚拟现实技术提供了广阔的应用前景。美国国防部高级研究计划局DARPA自80年代起一直致力于研究称为SIMNET的虚拟战场系统，以提供坦克协同训1练，该系统可联结200多台模拟器。利用虚拟现实技术模拟战争过程已成为最先进的多快好省的研究战争、培训指挥员的方法。战争实验室在检验预定方案用于实战方面也能起巨大作用。1991年海湾战争开始前，美军便把海湾地区各种自然环境和伊拉克军队的各种数据输入计算机内，进行各种作战方案模拟后才定下初步作战方案。后来实际作战的发展和模拟实验结果相当一致。\r\n商业虚拟现实技术常被用于推销。例如建筑工程投标时，把设计的方案用虚拟现实技术表现出来，便可把业主带入未来的建筑物里参观，如门的高度、窗户朝向、采光多少、屋内装饰等，都可以感同身受。它同样可用于旅游景点以及功能众多、用途多样的商品推销。因为用虚拟现实技术展现这类商品的魅力，比单用文字或图片宣传更加有吸引力。\r\n科技开发虚拟现实技术可缩短开发周期，减少费用。例如克莱斯勒公司1998年初便利用虚拟现实技术，在设计某两种新型车上取得突破，首次使设计的新车直接从计算机屏幕投入生产线，也就是说完全省略了中间的试生产。由于利用了卓越的虚拟现实技术，使克莱斯勒避免了1500项设计差错，节约了8个月的开发时间和8000万美元费用。利用虚拟现实技术还可以进行汽车冲撞试验，不必使用真的汽车便可显示出不同条件下的冲撞后果。\r\n在虚拟现实技术已经和理论分析、科学实验一起，成为人类探索客观世界规律的三大手段。用它来设计新材料，可以预先了解改变成分对材料性能的影响。在材料还没有制造出来之前便知道用这种材料制造出来的零件在不同受力情况下是如何损坏的。\r\n以上仅列出虚拟现实技术的部分应用前景，可以预见，在不久的将来，虚拟现实技术将会影响甚至改变我们的观念与习惯，并将深入到人们的日常工作与生活。\r\n6、总结\r\n虚拟现实技术是本世纪发展的重要技术之一，作为一门科学和艺术将会不断走向成熟，在各行各业中将得到广泛应用，并发挥神奇的作用，二十一世纪将是虚拟现实技术的时代。\r\n当然，虚拟现实技术还是一门年轻的科学技术，尚存在不少有待解决的问题。例如，在计算机生成的虚拟环境中，操每次转动头部，计算机必须更新三维图像，由于更新的数据太大，以致计算机还无法完成实时运算。这就造成了系统滞后。再如，美空军的虚拟现实模拟器产生的视觉运动信号与人的感觉之间也存在差异，轻易引起头痛、眩晕等。\r\n但不管怎样，虚拟现实技术究竟开辟了富有发展潜力的新领域，它会随着时间的推移日臻完善，发挥的作用也将会越来越大。\r\n7、参考文献\r\n1李云华虚拟现实技术综述重型机械科技2004\r\n2张志鹏劳奇成虚拟现实技术的概况及应用精密制造与自动化2005\r\n3谢晶妮张茂军虚拟现实发展趋势展望计算机工程2002\r\n4郑彦平贺钧虚拟现实技术的应用现状及发展信息技术2005\r\n5刘耀林孔建益蒋国璋孙亮波虚拟现实技术的发展湖北工业大学学2005\r\n6周红军王选科虚拟现实系统概述航空计算技术2005', 'Abstract: virtual reality technology is only a rise of the twentieth century brand-new comprehensive information technology, rapid development in recent years, its application field design to education, military, entertainment and medical and many other industries. This paper Outlines the concept of virtual reality technology, basic features and technical classification, puts forward the virtual reality technology development, expounds the technical bottleneck of virtual reality technology application and advantages.\r\n\r\nKeywords: virtual reality; Immersed; Interactive; Imagine;\r\n\r\nVirtualReality; Immersion; Interaction; Made of\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology concepts\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology is a comprehensive integration technology, it is the emergence of the computer graphics, human-machine interaction, the sensor technology, man-machine interface technology and artificial intelligence technology, the result of crossing and comprehensive. It use computer to generate lifelike 3d vision, hearing, smell, etc. Various kinds of feeling, the user through the appropriate devices, naturally to virtual reality world experience and interaction. Say simply, the virtual reality technology is to use computers create real world.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology characteristics\r\n\r\nIn 1993 BurdeaG Electro93 international conference in the "VirtualRealitySystemandApplication", and puts forward a text of virtual reality technology three features, namely: immersed sense, alternation, imaginary.\r\n\r\nImmersed sense is that users can immerse yourself in computer-generated virtual environment and generated by computer user input to the ability of virtual scene, the user in the virtual scene has "illustrates the landscapes" feeling. It see, hear, smell, touch, completely and true feelings in the environment of the same. It is the core of virtual reality system.\r\n\r\nInteractive user and the virtual scene refers to various object interaction skills. It is a key factor in the man-machine harmony. Users into virtual environment, through a variety of sensors and diversification information environment, the user can occur interaction necessary operation, the virtual environment make corresponding response, also with real, like in a virtual environment picked up basketball, you can feel the weight of the ball and threw it on the ground can bounce. Interactive includes an object operable degree and the user to get feedback from the environment of natural degree, virtual scene object according to the laws of physics degree of motion, for example, when the object is force, the object will move along the direction of emphatically, turn to or from the desktop to the ground, etc.\r\n\r\nImaginary is through the user immersed in a "real" virtual environment, and virtual environments, the various interaction from qualitative and quantitative integrated environment for the perceptual and the rational knowledge, which can deepen the concept, germination of new, produce familiar leap. Therefore, the virtual reality is more than just a user with a terminal user interfaces, and can be immersed in obtaining new knowledge in this environment, improve the perceptual and the rational familiar, resulting in new ideas. This idea results system, input into the system will process after the state real-time display or by sensing device feedback to the user. So again, this is a learning - creation - to learn -- and then the creative process, thus can say, virtual reality is to inspire people''s creative thinking activity.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology classification\r\n\r\nVirtual Reality VirtualReality a word from the English translation, the meaning of order is false, Reality is real meaning, combined to is Virtual Reality, i.e. were not things and environment, through the various technical Virtual out, let you feel like real life.\r\n\r\nThe actual application of virtual reality system can be divided into four categories:\r\n\r\nA, desktop virtual reality system, also called the virtual reality window. It can be realized by desktop machines, so the cost is low, the simplest, function also is mainly used for CAD, CAM, architectural design, desktop games, etc.\r\n\r\nSecond, immersed virtual reality system, such as various USES experience device, make the person has the feeling of immersive, various training, demonstration and senior games purposes are available this system.\r\n\r\nThree, virtual reality system, it in the Internet environment, make full use of the local resources, distribution of the development of virtual reality utilization. It is usually myself virtual reality system development, also is distributed in different places of the virtual reality system, immersion connected via the Internet to accomplish some purposes. The United States NPSNet large military interactive simulation system and the Internet multiplayer MUD is this kind of system.\r\n\r\nFour, augmented reality mixed reality system, say again. It is the true environment and virtual environment combining system, which can reduce the spending constitutes a complex environment, but also to the actual operation, the real object reached esthetic state, it is the direction of future development.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology development bottleneck\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology in the development process of the many problems, encounter boils down to the three major problems:\r\n\r\n4.1 virtual reality equipment "changed". To build a high quality virtual reality system, we first need to expensive external equipment, either high resolution, or the helmet display HMD stereo projection display, whether space locator, or high-precision data glove, all is the price does not poor. Secondly, to complete complicated scene real-time rendering, still require high-performance graphics workstations and the corresponding software. In some special field, but ordinary information system users may flinch.\r\n\r\n4.2 trival 3d modeling. Based on the graphic virtual environments first problems to solve is three-dimensional modelling. When rendering graphics technology to achieve realism in the great strides, the process of generating accurate 3d models like 20 years ago as difficult. In 3d laser scanning technology provides the simplified model the progress of some of the promised tectonic processes. However, these automation model acquisition method also verified real world geometry is extremely complicated. Most of the model still need artificially drawing, and need to hire a high level of professionals, so the cost is quite amazing. For instance in the film, ", tank Nick for realizing scene of 3d modeling and various special processing spends artificially cost as much as $25 million, the money is enough to make a ship''s boat. Same size Trival 3d modeling is also restricted the virtual reality technology development serious obstacle.\r\n\r\n4.3 large amount of data. Virtual reality technology to get great development, need, perhaps with Internet combination already is the fact that does not dispute. At present the virtual reality technology application is very large still, the amount of data in the existing network overall slower, Internet users must wait for a long time, this often was unbearable. We should consider in virtual reality system data compression problem, this problem may now have not yet attracted people''s attention, but as the application deeply, this is an unavoidable problem.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology application prospect and advantage\r\n\r\nThe application of virtual reality technology is widely Helsel and Doherty, in 1993 on the worldwide have been almost 805 of the virtual reality research project, the results indicate that the current statistics of education and art in entertainment, application of mainstream, secondly is occupied military and aerospace, medicine, business, in addition in computing visualization, manufacturing, etc have considerable proportion. Below is a brief introduction to its partial application.\r\n\r\nMedical virtual reality technology application generally has two kinds. One is the virtual human body, also is the digital human, such human model of the human body more easily understand doctor structures and functions. Another is the virtual operation system, can be used to guide of the operation.\r\n\r\nSatara Pieper and researchers in the early 1990s as based on two SGI workstation created a virtual surgery, used in the legs and trainers abdominal surgery simulation. This virtual environment including virtual operating table with surgical lamp, virtual surgery tools, virtual model of the human body and the organ, etc. By HMD and feel gloves, user can virtual model of the human body for surgery. But the system is further improved, such as the need to improve the environmental effects of, increase network function, make its can also training multiple users, or may be under the guidance of experts in the field work, etc.\r\n\r\nEntertainment, art and education rich feel ability and 3D display environment makes virtual reality technology to become the ideal video game tools. Because of the virtual reality in entertainment high demand is not the reality, so in recent years of virtual reality technology in this aspect development most rapidly. Such as Chicago opened the world''s first large-scale available for people using virtual reality entertainment systems, its theme is about 3025 years of a future war; British development called "Virtuality" virtual reality gaming systems, equipped with HMD greatly enhances the realism; In 1992 LegealQust "a called" the system by increasing the artificial intelligence function, make the computer has the self-learning function greatly enhances the interest and the difficulty and make the system won this year virtual reality product award;\r\n\r\nMilitary and aerospace industry practice has been simulated and military and aerospace industry, an important subject for the virtual reality technology to provide a broad application prospects. U.S. defense advanced research projects agency DARPA since the 1980s has been devoted to the study of virtual battle system called SIMNET collaborative training, to provide tanks practice, this system can one more than 200 sets connecting the simulator. Using virtual reality technology simulated war have become the most advanced process of how fast the provincial research method of war, training commanders. In war lab for actual combat inspection reservation scheme has a huge role. Before the start of the gulf war in 1991, the U.S. gave the gulf various natural environment and the Iraqi army''s various enter data into the computer, in order to simulate various battle plan only after preliminary battle plan set. Later the development of practical operation consistent and experimental results.\r\n\r\nCommercial virtual reality technology are often used to sell. For example, the architectural engineering bidding the scheme design with virtual reality technology expression comes out, can put the owner into the future in buildings, such as the height of the visit, window door toward, daylighting is much, house decoration, can empathy. It also can be used for tourism attractions and function, USES the many diverse selling products. Because using virtual reality technology show the charm of this kind of goods than words or pictures alone, more attractive propaganda.\r\n\r\nTechnology development virtual reality technology can shorten the development cycle, reducing costs. For example Chrysler in early 1998, then using virtual reality technology in design of two new car a breakthrough first make a design new car, directly from the computer screen into production line, that is completely omitted in the middle of the trial production. Because of using outstanding virtual reality technology, make Chrysler avoid 1,500, saved a design mistakes 8 months development time and $80 million fee. Using virtual reality technology also can undertake car crash tests, need not use really can be show car collision under different conditions consequences.\r\n\r\nIn the virtual reality technology has and theoretical analysis, scientific experiments together, become a human exploration of the three means objective world rule. Use it to design new materials, can advance knowledge of material change its composition properties. In material haven''t made out with this material before they know the parts made in different loading cases is how to damage.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology listed above is only part of the application prospect, predictable, in the near future, the virtual reality technology will influence or even change our ideas and habits, and will further to People''s Daily work and life.\r\n\r\n6, summarizes\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology is one of the most important technologies in this century development, as a science and art will continue in all walks of maturity, and will be widely applied, and play a magical effect, the 21st century will be the virtual reality technology era.\r\n\r\nOf course, the virtual reality technology or a young science and technology, and there are still many problems which need to be solved. For example, in computer-generated virtual environment, fuck every turn head, the computer must update 3d images, because update data too big, so that the computer is still unable to complete the real-time operation. This created the system lag. Be like again, the air force virtual reality simulator produce visual movement between signal and people the feeling is different, easy cause headaches, dizziness, etc.\r\n\r\nBut anyway, the virtual reality technology actually opened up a new field of rich development potential, it will with the passage of time, the role of being perfected and will grow larger.\r\n\r\n7 and references\r\n\r\n1 LiYunHua virtual reality technology overview heavy machinery technology 2004\r\n\r\n2 ZhangZhiPeng LaoJi into virtual reality technology of the general situation and application precision manufacturing and automation 2005\r\n\r\n3 XieJingNi ZhangMaoJun virtual reality development trend expectation, computer engineering 2002\r\n\r\n4 ZhengYanPing HeJun virtual reality technology application situation and the development of information technology, 2005\r\n\r\n5 LiuYaoLin KongJianYi JiangGuoZhang SunLiang wave virtual reality technology development hubei university of technology to learn 2005\r\n\r\n6 ZhouGongJun WangXuanKe virtual reality system outline aviation computing 2005 ', '../pic/2011052428987_20090310105723953.jpg', '综述虚拟现实技术及其应用', 'Virtual reality technology and its application were reviewed ', '', 13);
INSERT INTO `20article` (`id`, `itm_id`, `title_chs`, `title_eng`, `username`, `date`, `content_chs`, `content_eng`, `pic`, `picdesc_chs`, `picdesc_eng`, `fileupload`, `click_throughs`) VALUES
(132, 60, '关于对虚拟现实发展及现状的探析', 'About virtual reality development and current situation of the article ', 'admin', '2011-05-24', '　论文关键词：虚拟现实 现状 发展趋势\r\n　　论文摘要：介绍了虚拟现实技术的概念、基本特征与类型，并从虚拟现实技术的特点和应用出发，论述虚拟现实技术在各个领域的应用，并针对虚拟现实技术的现状和发展趋势进行了简单分析。\r\n　　\r\n　　随着科学技术的迅猛发展，虚拟现实技术成为近几年来国内外科技界关注的一个热点，它的兴起，为人机交互界面的发展开创了新的研究领域，为各类工程的大规模数据可视化提供了新的描述方法。目前，虚拟现实技术已广泛应用于航空航天、医学实习、军事训练、建筑设计、教育培训等众多领域。\r\n　　\r\n　　一、虚拟现实分类\r\n　　\r\n　　根据用户参与的形式的不同，通常把虚拟现实分成四大类。桌面虚拟现实，沉浸的虚拟现实，增强现实性的虚拟现实，分布式虚拟现实。\r\n　　（一）桌面虚拟现实\r\n　　桌面虚拟现实（PCVR）系统，基本上是一套基于普通PC平台的小型桌面虚拟现实系统。 其实就是使用个人计算机即PC机或PC工作站去产生仿真，桌面虚拟现实的参与者是不完全沉浸的，他要求参与者使用标准的CRT显示器和立体显示技CJFD2000以及位置跟踪器和另外一个手控输入设备，如数据手套和六个自由度的三维空间鼠标器，戴上立体眼镜坐在监视器前，在一些专业软件的帮助下，但可以通过计算机屏幕观察360度范围内的虚拟境界。\r\n　　（二）沉浸的虚拟现实\r\n　　沉浸式虚拟现实系统是一种高级的虚拟现实系统，它提供一个完全沉浸的体验，使用户有一种置身于虚拟境界之中的感觉。它利用头盔式显示器或其它设备，把参与者的视觉、听觉和其它感觉封闭起来，并提供一个新的、虚拟的感觉空间，并利用位置跟踪器、数据手套、其它手控输入设备、声音等使得参与者产生一种身临其境、全心投入和沉浸其中的感觉。沉浸式虚拟系统是一套比较复杂的系统，它的优点是使用户全身心地沉浸到虚拟世界中去，缺点是系统设备价格昂贵，难以普及推广。\r\n　　（三）增强现实性的虚拟现实\r\n　　 增强式虚拟现实系统是把真实环境和虚拟环境组合在一起的一种系统，它既允许用户看到真实世界，同时也可以看到叠加在真实世界的虚拟对象，这种系统既可减少对构成复杂真实环境的计算，又可对实际物体进行操作，真正达到亦真亦幻的境界。\r\n　　（四）分布式虚拟现实\r\n　　分布式虚拟现实系统是利用远程网络，将异地的不同用户联结起来，多个用户通过网络同时参加一个虚拟空间，共同体验虚拟经历，对同一虚拟世界进行观察和操作，达到协同工作的目的，从而将虚拟现实的应用提升到了一个更高的境界。\r\n　　\r\n　　二、国内外虚拟现实的发展及其现状\r\n　　\r\n　　（一）美国研究状况\r\n　　美国作为VR技术的发源地，其研究水平基本上就代表国际VR发展的水平。近年来,虚拟现实在美国航空航天和军事领域的若干成功应用所获得的巨大经济效益和社会效益，促使美国政府进一步加大了对虚拟现实技术研究的支持力度。在美国虚拟现实在以下三个方面发挥重大作用：（1）武器系统性能评价；（2）武器操纵训练；（3）指挥大规模军事演习。虚拟现实的应用将大幅度降低以上三者所需的费用，极大地提高效益，并消除意外伤亡事故。美国政府所支持的虚拟现实研究也正是紧紧围绕着提供这三种能力的系统和环境而展开的。\r\n　　在军事领域，美国的主要研究单位为：美国空军技术研究所(Air Force Institute of Technology)主要研究人类因素的检测、计算机图形学以及与大规模分布综合环境应用有关的人机交互问题，尤其对那些培养实际操作人员的环境感兴趣。这些环境的特点是有明确的目的性、大规模、复杂及主动性。有目的性的含义是在环境中的活动者具有明确的目标，并主动采取行动来达到这些目标。海军研究生院图形和图像实验室(Naval Postgraduate School Graphics and Video laboratory)的研究目标是为基于网络化虚拟环境的交互仿真开发低价格模拟器。他们正在研制一种便宜的、实时网络化的飞行模拟器NPSNET4。它使用SIMNET和分布式交互仿真两种协议进行主机之间的通信。NPSNET计划注意虚拟世界的系统在现实世界问题中的应用。美国陆军研究所(U.S.Army Research Institute)从事虚拟环境的行为科学和计算机科学两方面的研究,并在美国陆军委员会支持下的用于战斗训练的仿真电子战场的应用中发挥着重要作用。密西根大学(University of Michigan)承担了SOAR项目，其目的是要通过提供改进了的空仿真兵力来扩充LORAL MODSAF。这一计划将使美国国防部在虚拟战役仿真中具有智能化的和难以战胜的敌方战机具备时态推理能力、多目标管理和传感能力，使管理和操纵敌方兵力的人减至最少。\r\n　在航天领域，现在NASA已经建立了航空、卫星维护VR训练系统，空间站VR训练系统，并且已经建立了可供全国使用的VR教育系统。北卡罗来纳大学(UNC)的计算机系是进行VR研究最早的大学，他们主要研究分子建模、航空驾驶、外科手术仿真、建筑仿真等。\r\n　　美国政府对虚拟现实技术非常重视，他们支持的虚拟现实研究计划都是面向航空航天和军事应用的。虚拟现实将在武器系统的性能评价和设计、操纵训练和大规模军事演习及战役指挥方面发挥重要作用，并产生巨大的经济效益。美国已初步建成了一些洲际范围的分布式虚拟环境，并将有人操纵和半自主兵力引入虚拟的战役空间，,在世界上处于领先地位。\r\n　　（二）中国研究现状\r\n　　我国VR技术研究起步较晚，与国外发达国家还有一定的差距，但现在已引起国家有关部门和科学家们的高度重视，并根据我国的国情，制定了开展VR技术的研究计划。九五规划、国家自然科学基金委、国家高技术研究发展计划等都把VR列入研究项目。\r\n　　国内一些重点院校，已积极投入到了这一领域的研究工作。北京航空航天大学计算机系是国内最早进行VR研究、最有权威的单位之一，着重研究了虚拟环境中物体物理特性的表示与处理；实现了分布式虚拟环境网络设计，虚拟现实应用系统的开发平台等。浙江大学开发出了一套桌面型虚拟建筑环境实时漫游系统，还研制出了在虚拟环境中一种新的快速漫游算法和一种递进网格的快速生成算法；哈尔滨工业大学已经成功地虚拟出了人的高级行为中特定人脸图像的合成、表情的合成和唇动的合成等技术问题。\r\n　　虚拟现实技术在我国近些年发展极为迅速，被广泛的应用在城市规划、教育培训、文物保护、医疗、房地产、互联网、勘探测绘、生产制造、军事航天等数十个重要的行业，全世界的目光都聚焦于虚拟现实技术在中国的蓬勃发展。流行一时的网络游戏，实质上也是虚拟现实技术的一种简单应用。\r\n　　最近，中国首款虚拟现实游戏射日精英也已经横空出世。\r\n　　 　　\r\n　　纵观多年来的发展历程，VR技术的未来研究仍将遵循“低成本、高性能”这一原则，从软件、硬件上展开，并将在以下主要方向发展：\r\n　　动态环境建模技术。动态环境建模技术的目的是获取实际环境的三维数据，并根据需要建立相应的虚拟环境模型。\r\n　　实时三维图形生成和显示技术。在不降低图形的质量和复杂程度的前提下，如何提高刷新频率将是今后重要的研究内容。此外，现有的虚拟设备还不能满足系统的需要，有必要开发新的三维图形生成和显示技术。\r\n　　新型交互设备的研制。虚拟现实需要头盔显示器、数据手套、数据衣服、三维位置传感器和三维声音产生器等。因此，新型、便宜、做工精良的数据手套和数据服将成为未来研究的重要方向。\r\n　　智能化语音虚拟现实建模。虚拟现实建模如果将VR技术与智能技术、语音识别技术结合起来将会给虚拟现实的发展带来巨大的意义。\r\n　　大型网络分布式虚拟现实(Distributed Virtual Reality，DVR)的应用。目前，分布式虚拟交互仿真已成为国际上的研究热点，相继推出了DIS、MA等相关标准。网络分布式VR在航天中极具应用价值，例如，国际空间站的参与国分布在世界不同区域，分布式VR训练环境不需要在各国重建仿真系统，这样不仅减少了研制费设备费用，而且也减少了人员出差的费用和异地生活的不适。\r\n　　\r\n　　结语\r\n　　\r\n　　虚拟现实从其萌芽到今天的日渐成熟已经经历了一段相当长的时间，伴随着计算机图像技术和计算机网络技术的不断发展，我们的虚拟现实技术也将迎来一个快速发展的阶段，使我们的虚拟现实中的场景更加真实，虚拟显示中的人物也更加形象生动，成为一个真正意义上的“人”。\r\n　　\r\n　　参考文献\r\n　　[1]胡小强．虚拟现实技术[M].北京：机械工业出版社，2005．\r\n　　[2]黄明吉．虚拟数控技术及应用[M].北京：化学工业出版社，2005.\r\n　　[3]蒋庆全．国外VR技术发展综述[J]．飞航导弹，2002，(1)． ', 'Papers keywords: virtual reality status development trend\r\n\r\nAbstract: this paper introduces vr technology concepts, basic characteristics and types, and virtual reality technology from the characteristics and application of virtual reality technology, expounds the application in different fields and virtual reality technology in the present situation and development trend of a simple analysis.\r\n\r\nAlong with the rapid development of scientific technology, the virtual reality technology to become in recent years involving concern at home and abroad, it''s a hot rise, for the development of the man-machine interface blazed a new research field, for all types of engineering of large-scale data visualization provided new description method. At present, the virtual reality technology has been widely used in aerospace, medical practice, military training, architecture design, education training, etc.\r\n\r\nA, virtual reality classification\r\n\r\nAccording to the different forms of user participation, usually divided into four categories of the virtual reality. Desktop virtual reality, immersed virtual reality, enhance realism virtual reality, virtual reality.\r\n\r\n(a) desktop virtual reality\r\n\r\nDesktop virtual reality (PCVR) system, is basically a set of ordinary PC platform based on the small desktop virtual reality system. In fact is the use of personal computer namely PC or PC workstation to produce simulation, desktop virtual reality of participants is not completely lost, he asked participants to use the standard CRT monitor and stereo display technology CJFD2000 and position tracker and another manual control input device, such as data glove and six degrees of freedom of 3d mouse, wear the stereo glasses before sitting in some professional monitor software under the help, but can be observed by computer screen 360 degrees within the scope of the virtual realm.\r\n\r\n(2) immersed virtual reality\r\n\r\nTele-immersive virtual reality system is an advanced virtual reality system, which provides a completely immersed experience, users have a kind of place oneself in the virtual realm of feeling. It used TouKuiShi display or other equipment, the participants'' vision, hearing and other feeling closed up, and provide a new, virtual feeling space, and by position tracker, data glove, other hand control input devices, sounds, etc, make the participants to produce a scene and devotion and immerse inside feeling. Tele-immersive virtual system is a complex system, its advantage is the user wholeheartedly immersed in the virtual world, defect is expensive, system equipment to popularize.\r\n\r\n(3) enhance realism virtual reality\r\n\r\nReinforcement virtual reality system is to put a real environment and virtual environment together a system, it already allows users to see the real world, also can see superimposed on the virtual objects in the real world, this system not only can reduce the real environment to constitute a complex calculation, but also to the actual object operation, the truly achieve the esthetic border.\r\n\r\n(4) distributed virtual reality\r\n\r\nVirtual reality system is using remote network, will link together different different users, multiple users through the network also attend a virtual space, experience together on the same virtual experience a virtual world, observing and operation, achieve the purpose of collaborative work, and the application of virtual reality will be promoted to a higher level.\r\n\r\nSecond, the development of domestic and international virtual reality and its present status\r\n\r\n(a) the United States study condition\r\n\r\nThe United States as the birthplace of the VR technique, the research level is basically represent international VR development level. In recent years, virtual reality in the U.S. aerospace and military field obtained several successful application of great economic benefits and social benefits, prompting the U.S. government to further increase the virtual reality technology support. In the United States virtual reality in the following three aspects: (1) plays a major role weapon system performance evaluation; (2) weapons manipulation of training; (3) command massive military drill. The application of virtual reality will greatly reduce the costs required for all three, greatly improve efficiency, and to eliminate accident casualties. The us government support virtual reality research is also closely around the offer this three kinds of ability of the system and environment to launch.\r\n\r\nIn military field is the main research unit, the United States for: the United States Air Force Technology Institute (Air Force major research Institute of Technology) human factors detection, computer graphics and comprehensive environmental application with large-scale distribution related human-computer interaction problems, especially for those who cultivate practical operation personnel are interested in the environment. These environmental features a definite purpose, large, complex and initiative. Purposefully meaning is in the environment of activists have clear objectives, and actively take action to achieve these goals. The Naval Postgraduate School in monterey, Graphics and image Naval Postgraduate laboratories (laboratory) little Video and used for the objectives of the study is based on the interactive simulation net virtual environment developing low price simulator. They are developing a cheap, real-time network NPSNET4 flight simulators. It USES SIMNET and distributed interactive simulation two protocols of communication between the host. NPSNET program note the virtual world of system in the real world application problems. U.S. army Research Institute (U.S.A rmy Institute) true the behavior of virtual environment in two aspects of science and computer science, and the American army committee support for combat training simulation electronic battlefield application plays an important role. University of Michigan (of the Michigan) leads for SOAR project, its aim is to provide improved through the empty simulation MODSAF LORAL forces to expand. This plan will make U.S. defense in virtual battle simulation has intelligent and difficult against enemy warplanes have tense reasoning ability, multi-objective management and sensing ability, make management and manipulation of enemy forces minimized.\r\n\r\nNow in spaceflight, NASA has established airlines, satellite maintenance VR training system, the space station, and have been training system of VR established for the national education system using VR. North Carolina university (UNC) computer department is the earliest university research on VR, they mainly study molecular modeling, aviation driving, surgical simulation, building simulation, etc.\r\n\r\nThe U.S. government attaches great importance to the virtual reality technology of virtual reality, they support research plan are facing the aerospace and military applications. Virtual reality will be in weapon system of performance evaluation, and design, manipulate the training and large-scale military exercise and play an important role in campaign command, and produce the huge economic benefits. The United States has initially build some intercontinental range of distributed virtual environment, and someone will manipulate and half the battle to introduce a virtual independent force in world space,, a leading position.\r\n\r\n(2) China research situation\r\n\r\nOur VR technology research, and started late abroad developed countries, there is still a gap, but now has caused the relevant state departments and scientists are highly valued, and formulated according to China''s national condition, carrying out the VR technique research plan. The ninth planning, the national natural science JiJinWei, national high technology research and development program the VR included in such research projects.\r\n\r\nSome domestic key universities, has been aggressively into this field of research. Beijing university of aeronautics on computer department is the earliest and most authoritative research VR, focused on the research of the units in virtual environment objects of physical characteristics and processing; says Realized in distributed virtual environment network design, virtual reality application system development platform, etc. Zhejiang university developed a set of desktop virtual building environment real-time roaming system, also developed a new virtual environment in rapid roaming algorithm and a progressive grid fast generation algorithms; Harbin industrial university has successfully virtual out people''s senior behavior specific face image synthesis of the synthesis, expression and lip dynamic synthesis technology.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology in our country is very rapidly in recent years development, by widespread application in the urban planning, the education training, cultural relic protection, medical care, real estate, Internet, exploration surveying and mapping, manufacturing, military spaceflight dozens of important industry, the eyes of the world are focused on virtual reality technology in China''s booming. Pop moment of network game, virtual reality technology is virtually a simple application.\r\n\r\nRecently, China''s first virtual reality game shoot day elite has also emerged was born.\r\n\r\nThroughout the years development course, VR technique future research will still follow the "low cost, high performance" from this principle, hardware, software, and will spread out in the main direction:\r\n\r\nDynamic environment modeling. Dynamic environment modeling to get practical environment, and according to the 3d data need to establish the corresponding virtual environment model.\r\n\r\nReal-time 3d graphics generation and display technology. Without lowering the quality and complexity of graphics, the premise of how to improve the frequency will refresh the is the important research content. In addition, the existing virtual equipment can''t satisfy the system needs, it is necessary to develop new 3d graphics generation and display technology.\r\n\r\nNew interactive device. Virtual reality needs helmet display, data glove, data clothes, three-dimensional position sensor and 3d sound generator, etc. Therefore, new, cheaper, works excellent data glove and data service will become an important direction of future research.\r\n\r\nIntelligent pronunciation virtual reality modeling. Virtual reality modeling if will VR technique and intelligent technology, voice recognition technology combine will give virtual reality development bring great significance.\r\n\r\nLarge network Virtual Reality (DVR), Distributed insgroupsto Reality of application. At present, the distributed virtual interactive simulation has become the international research hotspot, launched the DIS, MA and other related standards. Network distributed VR in space the most application value, such as the international space station, participating countries distribution in different regions of the world were distributed VR training environment, all countries do not need to be in, which is not only a reconstruction of the simulation system is developed fee equipment cost reduction, and also reduce the cost and different personnel travel the discomfort of life.\r\n\r\nepilogue\r\n\r\nVirtual reality from its sprout to today''s maturity has experienced a long period of time, with computer image technology and computer network technology unceasing development, our virtual reality technology will usher in a rapid development stage, make our virtual reality of scene more real, virtual display characters are more vivid and become a real sense of "man".\r\n\r\nreferences\r\n\r\n[1] HuXiaoJiang. Virtual reality technology [M].beijing: machinery industry press, 2005.\r\n\r\n[2]. HuangMingJi virtual nc technology and application [M].beijing: chemical industry press, 2005.\r\n\r\n[3] JiangQing all foreign VR technique were reviewed. The development [J].j maneuverable missile, 2002, (1). ', '../pic/2011052498346_qibeng.jpg', '关于对虚拟现实发展及现状的探析', 'About virtual reality development and current situation of the article ', '', 6),
(133, 30, '虚拟设计环境系统中虚拟现实技术的研究', 'Virtual design environment system in virtual reality technology research ', 'admin', '2011-05-24', '虚拟现实技术是计算机图形学、人工智能、计算机网络、信息处理等技术综合发展的产物。虚拟现实技术在机械行业有广泛的应用前景。面向装配的设计是当前研究的一个热点。 本论文以虚拟设计系统的研究、开发为切入点，对其中相关的虚拟现实技术进行了研究、分析，既有理论方面的又有实践方面的。 立体显示设备在虚拟现实系统中占具重要位置，为系统提供立体视觉，其购置成本较高。本文提出的基于双机通信的立体显示技术用软件的复杂度来代替硬件的复杂度，降低了成本，是立体显示技术的新发展。 基于虚实跳变的混合建模技术是一种基于图形图象的混合建模技术。该技术可以在虚拟环境中把图象当作前景来处理。其关键算法是虚境交互算法、虚实跳变算法。基于图象建模中存在着难以同图象中物体进行交互、交互过程中图形图象融合的问题。虚境交互算法对虚境中物体以图象的形式进行处理，使用ID号标识的方法来管理物体和实现交互。虚实跳变算法对跳变物体同时进行虚境交互、实境交互两种处理，采用外露面投影的方法来实现图形、图象的相互融合，达到了虚实无缝连接的效果。 装配规划中存在着不考虑装配的阶段性、过程性和可并行性的问题。基于VRML的虚拟装配过程仿真采用了二次规划、行为仿真、控制过程，达到了更真实更清晰地反映装配过程的效果。二次规划利用零部件和子装配体的位置信息、可并行性来对装配进行再次规划，实现装配的过程性和可并行性。利用运动学方法、关系法来实现行为仿真和控制过程，在控制过程中实现了指示信息，对装配实现的阶段性、过程性进行了控制。', 'Virtual reality technology is computer graphics, artificial intelligence, computer network, information processing technology comprehensive development of product. Virtual reality technology in mechanical industry has broad prospect of application. Design for assembly is a hotspot of current research. This paper presents the design of the system research, development as the breakthrough point, on which the virtual reality technology related to the research, analysis, both theoretical and practical. Three-dimensional display devices in virtual reality system has important position of system to provide stereo vision, their purchase cost is higher. In this paper, based on the dual machine communication with the stereo display technology to replace the complexity of the software of hardware complexity, reduced cost, is the new development of stereoscopic display technology. Based on the virtual jumping hybrid modeling technology is a kind of hybrid modeling based on graph technique. The technology can be the image in a virtual environment foreground to deal with as. Its key algorithm is virtual borders interactive algorithm, false or true jump to change algorithm. Based on image modeling to exist in interact with images objects, interactive process graph fusion problem. Virtual territory of virtual context interactive algorithm with the form of objects, with images using ID stickers to manage objects and realize interaction. Hopping algorithm for unionizing hopping objects simultaneously virtual interaction and reality interactive on two kinds of processing with external appearance projection way to implement graphics, image fusion of seamless connection, achieved the effect of unprotected. Assembly planning exist not consider assembly process and integrability stages and parallelism problem. Based on the virtual assembly process simulation of VRML using quadric programming, behavior simulation and control process more real, reached more clearly reflect the effect of the assembly process. Quadratic programming using parts and son the position information of entire assemblage, parallelism to assembly again, to implement assembly process planning sexual and can parallelism. Using the kinematics method, relations act to achieve behavior simulation and control process, in process control to realize the indication information, the process of assembling stages and realize the control of. ', '../pic/2011052457743_1343644.jpg', '虚拟设计环境系统中虚拟现实技术的研究', 'Virtual design environment system in virtual reality technology research ', '', 13),
(134, 10, '虚拟现实及其演变发展', 'Virtual reality and its evolution development ', 'admin', '2011-05-24', '摘要：本文首先简单介绍了虚拟现实技术，然后以几个在VR研究方面具有代表性的国家（主要是美国）为例，详述了VR的演变发展史。\r\n\r\n关键词：虚拟现实 研究现状 发展 技术\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n1 虚拟现实技术\r\n\r\n虚拟现实是从英文Virtual Reality一词翻译过来的。Virtual就是虚假的意思，Reality就是真实的意思，合并起来就是虚拟现实。国内也有人译为“灵境”或“幻真”。虚拟现实是一项融合了计算机图形学、人机接口技术、传感技术、心理学、人类工程学及人工智能的综合技术。\r\n\r\n目前，有关虚拟现实研究现状方面的资料很多，但关于这方面的记载都不够系统和全面，本文仅以几个具有典型性的国家为例，对其在VR方面的发展状况作一综述。\r\n\r\n2 美国的研究现状\r\n\r\n美国是在VR技术方面最具权威性的国家。美国VR研究技术的水平基本上就代表国际VR发展的水平。首先让我们先来回顾一下美国数十年来虚拟技术的发展历程。发展历程基本上可分为三个阶段： 20世纪 70年代以前为第一阶段；80年代初到80年代中期为第二阶段；第三阶段从80年代末期至今。\r\n\r\n2.1 虚拟现实技术思想的产生\r\n\r\n1929年，Edwin A.Link发明了飞行模拟器，使乘坐者的感觉和坐在真的飞机上是一样的。\r\n\r\n1956年，Morton Heileg开发了一个叫做Sensorama的摩托车仿真器。Sensorama具有三维显示及立体声效果，并能产生振动和风吹的感觉。\r\n\r\n1962年，Morton Heilig的专利“全传感仿真器”的发明，有振动、声的感觉。该专利也蕴涵了虚拟现实技术的思想。\r\n\r\n1965年计算机图形学的奠基者Ivan Sutherlan发表了“终极显示”(The Ultimate Display)的论文，提出了感觉真实、交互真实的人机协作新理论。\r\n\r\n1966年，美国的MIT林肯实验室在海军科研办公室的资助下，研制出了第一个头盔式显示器(HMD)，随后又将模拟力和触觉的反馈装置加入到系统中。\r\n\r\n1967年，美国北卡罗来纳大学开始了Grup计划，研究探讨力反馈(Force Feedback)装置。该装置可以将物理压力通过用户接口引向用户，可以使人感到一种计算机仿真力。\r\n\r\n1968年，Sutherlan在哈佛大学的组织下开发了头盔式立体显示器（Helmet Mounted Display 即HMD），后来他又开发了一个虚拟系统，可称得上是第一个虚拟现实系统。\r\n\r\n1970年，美国的MIT林肯实验室研制出了第一个功能较齐全的HMD系统。\r\n\r\n1973年年，Myron Krurger提出了“Artificial Reality”，这是早期出现的虚拟现实的词。\r\n2.2 虚拟现实技术初步发展\r\n\r\n20世纪80年代初到80年代中期。此阶段开始形成虚拟现实技术的基本概念。这一时期出现了两个比较典型的虚拟现实系统，即VIDEOPLACE与VIEW系统。\r\n\r\n20世纪80年代初，美国的DARPA（Defense Advenced Research Projects Agency）为坦克编队作战训练开发了一个实用的虚拟战场系统SIMNET。\r\n\r\n1984年，M.McGreevy和J.Humphries博士开发了虚拟环境视觉显示器，用于火星探测，将探测器发回地面的数据输入计算机，构造了火星表面的三维虚拟环境。\r\n\r\n1985年，WPAFB和Dean Kocian共同开发了VCASS飞行系统仿真器。\r\n\r\n1986年可谓硕果累累，Furness提出了一个叫作“虚拟工作台”(Virtual Crew station)的革命性概念；Robinett 与合作者 Fisher, Scott S, James Humphries, Michael McGreevy 发表了早期的虚拟现实系统方面的论文“The Virtual Environment Display System”；Jesse Eichenlaub提出开发一个全新的三维可视系统，其目标是使观察者不要那些立体眼镜、头跟踪系统、头盔等笨重的辅助东西也能达到同样效果的三维逼真的VR世界。这一愿望在1996年得以实现，因为有了2D/3D 转换立体显示器(DTI 3D display)的发明。\r\n\r\n1987年，James.D.Foley教授在具有影响力的《科学的美国》上发表了一篇题为先进的计算机界面（Interfaces for Advanced Computing）一文；美国《Scientific American》杂志还发表了一篇报导数据手套的文章，这篇文章及其后在各种报刊上发表的虚拟现实技术的文章引起了人们的极大兴趣。\r\n\r\n1989年，美国Jarn Lanier正式提出“Virtual Ｒeality(虚拟现实)”一词。\r\n\r\n2.3 虚拟现实技术的日趋完善\r\n\r\n1992年，Sense8公司开发了“WTK”开发包，为VR技术提供更高层次上的应用。\r\n\r\n1994年3月在日内瓦召开的第一届WWW大会上，首次正式提出了VRML这个名字。后来又出现了大量的VR建模语言，如：X3D，Java3D等。\r\n\r\n1994年，Burdea G和Coiffet出版了虚拟现实技术一书，在书中他用3I（Imagination、Interaction、Immersion）概括VR的三个基本特征。\r\n\r\n进入20世纪90年代，迅速发展的计算机软件、硬件系统使得基于大型数据集合的声音和图像的实时动画制作成为可能，越来越多的新颖、实用的输入输出设备相继进入市场，而人机交互系统的设计也在不断创新，这些都为虚拟现实系统的发展打下了良好的基础。其中，利用虚拟现实技术设计波音777获得成功，是近几年来又一件引起科技界瞩目的伟大成果。\r\n', 'Abstract: this paper briefly introduces the virtual reality technology, and then, with a few in VR research representative countries (mostly us) as an example, this paper expounds the evolution of VR history.\r\n\r\nKeywords: virtual reality research situation developing technology\r\n\r\n1 the virtual reality technology\r\n\r\nVirtual Reality is a word from English translation insgroupsto Reality. Insgroupsto is false mean, Reality is real meaning, combined to is Virtual Reality. Home also someone translated as "lingjinghutong to" or "unreal true". Virtual reality is a blend computer graphics, man-machine interface technology, sensing technology, psychology, ergonomics and artificially intelligent comprehensive technology.\r\n\r\nAt present, the research status on virtual reality, but many aspect of information about this aspect of records are not enough system and comprehensive, this article only on several typical country as a case, the development status of the VR aspects are reviewed in this paper.\r\n\r\n2 U.S. research status quo\r\n\r\nThe United States is in VR technology most authoritative countries. The level of U.S. VR technology basically have representative international VR development level. Let us first come first review of America for decades virtual technology development history. Development course can be divided into three stages: basically before 1970s for the first stage; In the early 1980s to the 1980s as the second stage; The third stage so far from the late 1980s.\r\n\r\n2.1 virtual reality technology thought produce\r\n\r\nIn 1929, Edwin A.L but invented the flight simulators, make those feelings and sat on the same plane is really.\r\n\r\nIn 1956, Morton Heileg developed a called Sensorama motorcycle emulator. Sensorama have 3d display and stereo effect, and can produce vibration breeze feeling.\r\n\r\nIn 1962, Morton Heilig patent "whole sensor simulators" invention, have the feeling of vibration and sound. This patent also contain the virtual reality technology thoughts.\r\n\r\n1965 The founders of The computer graphics Ivan Sutherlan published "Ultimate show" (The put The toll, and puts forward The thesis) feel real and interactive real human-machine cooperation new theory.\r\n\r\nIn 1966, American MIT Lincoln laboratory in the naval research office under the aid, developed the first TouKuiShi displays (HMD), then will simulation force and tactile feedback device to join into the system.\r\n\r\nIn 1967, American north Carolina university began Grup plan, study Force Feedback (Force Feedback) devices. This device can will physical pressure through the user interface to users, can make the person feels a computer simulation force.\r\n\r\nIn 1968, at Harvard University Sutherlan developed under the organization TouKuiShi stereo Display (Helmet HMD), put namely arrows and subsequently developed a virtual system, can be called the first virtual reality system.\r\n\r\nIn 1970, American MIT Lincoln laboratory developed the first function is more complete HMD system.\r\n\r\nYear after year Krurger Myron 1973, proposed "Artificial Reality", it is an early appear virtual Reality words.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology preliminary development 2.2\r\n\r\nIn the early 1980s to the 1980s. This stage started to form the basic concept of virtual reality technology. This period that the two comparatively typical virtual reality system, namely VIDEOPLACE and VIEW system.\r\n\r\nIn the early 1980s, America''s DARPA (Defense Projects Agency) Advenced true for tank formation combat training developed a practical virtual battle system SIMNET.\r\n\r\nIn 1984, M.M cGreevy and J.H dr umphries developed virtual environment, visual display unit for Mars, will probe back ground enter data into the computer, constructed on the surface of Mars 3d virtual environment.\r\n\r\nIn 1985, WPAFB and Dean Kocian common developed VCASS flight system emulator.\r\n\r\nIn 1986, it put forward Furness fruits called "Virtual workbench insgroupsto Crew revolutionary concept; now) Fisher, Scott Robinett and collaborators Humphries, Michael James S, published early McGreevy Virtual reality System in order to put The paper "views"; Jesse Eichenlaub to develop a new 3d visualization system, and its goal was to make the watchers don''t those stereo glasses, head tracking system, helmets, etc heavy auxiliary things can achieve the same effect 3d lifelike VR world. This desire in 1996 to achieve, because had the 2D / 3D conversion stereoscopic displays (DTI 3D put the invention.)\r\n\r\nIn 1987, D.F professor James. Oley in influential "scientific American published an article entitled, Advanced computer interface (Interfaces for Computing) are on the; The United States as the journal of others also published a report data glove articles, this article and in various newspapers after the virtual reality technology articles caused the people of great interest.\r\n\r\nIn 1989, U.S. Jarn Lanier officially proposed "insgroupsto Reality (Virtual Reality)" one word.\r\n\r\n2.3 virtual reality technology is perfected\r\n\r\nIn 1992, Sense8 company developed "WTK" provide for VR technology setups, higher levels of application.\r\n\r\nMarch 1994 in Geneva convention of the first WWW, the first official put forward the name of VRML. Then there appear a large number of VR modeling language, such as: Java3D X3D, etc.\r\n\r\nIn 1994, Coiffet Burdea G and published a book of virtual reality technology in the book he 3I Interaction, Immersion (made), three basic features generalizations VR.\r\n\r\nIn 1990''s, with the rapid development of computer software and hardware system based on large data set makes voice and image making possible the real-time animation, more and more of the novel, practical input and output devices have entered the market, and human-computer interaction system design also is in ceaseless innovation, all of these virtual reality system development have laid a good foundation. Among them, using the virtual reality technology design is successful, Boeing 777 in recent years and one of the great achievements involving high-profile caused. ', '../pic/2011052496890_FC1_SUC52917.jpg', '虚拟现实及其演变发展', 'Virtual reality and its evolution development ', '', 11);
INSERT INTO `20article` (`id`, `itm_id`, `title_chs`, `title_eng`, `username`, `date`, `content_chs`, `content_eng`, `pic`, `picdesc_chs`, `picdesc_eng`, `fileupload`, `click_throughs`) VALUES
(135, 60, '浅谈运用虚拟现实技术创建更和谐的教育环境', 'Discuss with virtual reality technology to create a more harmonious education environment ', 'admin', '2011-05-24', '　　论文关键词 ：虚拟现实技术应用  教育环境  教学效能\r\n　　论文摘要 ：利用计算机生成模拟环境的虚拟现实技术，能将三维空间的意念清楚地表述出来，使学习者直接、自然地与虚拟环境中的各种对象进行交互作用。桌面式虚拟技术成本较低，便于在教育领域广泛应用，它有利于创设新型的教学环境，强化学生学习的主体地位．激发学生学习的积极性和创造力，使教学获得事半功倍的效果。\r\n　　自20世纪 80年代以来，以多媒体技术、人机接口技术、传感技术和人工智能等学科为支撑的虚拟现实技术迅猛发展，逐渐渗透到经济、文化、军事以及人们生活等诸多方面，成为近年来国际科技界关注的一个热点。同时，虚拟现实技术也以极快的速度渗入教学领域，为教育的发展提供了一个极好的契机。对于教育事业来说，虚拟现实技术能将三维空间的意念清楚的表示出来，能使学习者直接、自然地与虚拟环境中的各种对象进行交互作用，并通过多种形式参与到事件的发展变化过程中去，从而获得最大的控制和操作整个环境的自由度。因此，该项技术的发展在很多教育与培训领域，具有明显的优势和特点。谋求虚拟现实技术更合理地应用于教育教学，为学习者创建更和谐的教育环境已成为一个新兴的教育研究课题。\r\n　　一、 虚拟现实技术应用于教学的原则\r\n　　(一)促学为本，实用为先\r\n　　所谓虚拟现实技术(virtuaI ReaIity，简称VR)，是指利用计算机生成一种模拟环境，并通过多种专用设备使用户 “投入”到该环境中，实现用户与该环境直接进行自然交互的技术；虚拟现实技术叮以让用户使用人的自然技能对世界中的物体进行考察或操作，同时提供视、听、摸等多种直观而又自然的实时感知。\r\n　　虚拟现实技术应用于教育教学将以促进学习者学习为根本目的，先进的技术手段也将服务于教学需求。随着虚拟现实技术自身的发展 ，已出现了多层次化的发展趋势，按其交互和浸入程度的不同可以被分为桌面式、沉浸式、叠加式和分布式虚拟现实系统等四类。其中桌面式的虚拟现实技术通过相对低廉的硬件产生较真实的效果 ，比较简单，需要投入的成本也不高，在教育领域内有着相当的发展远景，易于普及。桌面式虚拟现实技术仅使用个人计算机和低级工作站，把计算机的屏幕作为参与者观察虚拟环境的一个窗 口，使用简单 的外部设备(如：键盘、鼠标、力矩球、立体眼镜等)来驾驭虚拟环境和操纵虚拟物体。使学习者能够在虚拟的学习环境中扮演一个角色，全身心地投入到学习环境中去，这对他们的技能训练非常有利。利用虚拟现实技术，可以进行例如军事作战技能、外科手术技能、教学技能、体育技能、汽车驾驶技能、电器维修技能等各种职业技能的训练。由于这些虚拟的训练系统无任何危险，学习者可以反复练习，直至掌握操作技能为止。像北京航空航天大学计算机系虚拟现实与可视化新技术研究室在国家 863计划支持下 ，作为集成单位，与国防科技大学、浙江大学、装甲兵工程学院、中科院软件所和解放军测绘学院等单位一起建立 了一个用于虚拟现实技术研究和应用的分布式虚拟环境基础信息平台(DVENET)。在该平台中可以实现包含远程的数十个武器虚拟平台在同一块逼真地形下进行协同作业或对抗演练。参演人员 (即用户)可以通过不同的交互方式控制真实的或虚拟的武器仿真平台在虚拟战场环境中进行异地协同与对抗战术演练。\r\n　　虚拟现实技术实现了皮亚杰“把实验室搬到课堂上去”的设想与实践，也符合建构主义学习理论关于“学习是一种真实情境的体验”的观点。\r\n　　(二)乐用为本，适用为上\r\n　　尝试虚拟现实技术在教学中的运用，要求教师在教学设计中寻找到虚拟现实与教学的最佳结合点和切人点。虚拟现实技术运用于教学必须适当。目前来讲开发一个虚拟系统耗时费力，并不是件容易的事，而我们的教学也不是所有的内容都需要运用虚拟现实技术，可以从时间效能上优化选择，适合用多媒体技术的用多媒体 ，适合用虚拟现实技术的就用虚拟现实技术。 \r\n　　尝试在教学 中运用虚拟现实技术必须适度，教学内容和表现形式必须统一，还要注意给学习者留下足够的思考空间，运用不适当反而会使学习者沉浸在虚幻的世界中，难以自控。虚拟现实有其二重性：对于人的感官来说，它是真实存在的；对于所构造的物体来说 ，它又是不存在的。因此，能利用这一技术模仿许多高成本的、对人有危险的、或目前尚未出现的真实环境是极有价值的。例如，“仿真物理实验室”系统中，就使学生可以通过亲身实践——做、看、听的方式来学习。使用该系统，学生们可以停止时间的推移，以便仔细观察弹簧振子在关键点的运动轨迹随时间的变化过程；可以很容易的演示和控制物体的平抛运动的运动；还可以通过交互式数据模拟 “让小车沿长木板匀速运动”等各种实验，从而较深刻地理解物理概念和定律。虚拟现实技术应用于教学是一项全新的课题，没有多少现成的经验可以借鉴。但正因为没有经验，正因为困难重重，这个课题所拥有的创造空间必然是空前广阔的。 \r\n　　二、虚拟现实技术运用于教学的功能优势\r\n　　虚拟现实技术是计算机产生一种人为的空闯环境，通过多种专用设备让用户在视觉、听觉、触觉、嗅觉等多种感官上产生一种沉浸于虚拟环境的感觉。与传统的人机交互技术相比，虚拟现实具有三个最突出的特征 ：交互性、沉浸感和想象性。这些特征应用于教育中主要有以下方面突出的优势。 \r\n　　(一)创设 交互式学习环境，有利于促进学习方式的转变 \r\n　　《新课程标准 》强调学生学习方式的转变，积极倡导自主、合作、探究的学习方式，重视学生主动积极的参与意识和精神。运用虚拟现实技术计算机生成的学习环境，让学习者可以从自己的视点出发 ，利用 自然的技能和某些设备对这一生成的虚拟世界客体进行浏览和互动。这种技术方法不仅仅局限于常规的屏幕显示设备，而是多通道的人机交互模式，让学习者感觉似乎离开了自身所处的外部真实环境，已经沉浸在虚拟世界中，成为系统的组成部分。此时学习主要不是依赖教师的讲授，而是依靠学习者与环境的互动由学习者通过自身的感受 ，经过大脑思考和分析，形成目标实施策略，通过界面操作 ，系统接收信号，智能化地进行反馈，达到真正意义上的交互。这种探索性的学习，更有利于学习者进行自主的建构式学习。使人有可能从定性和定量综合集成的虚拟环境中得到感性和理性的认识，进而深化概念、产生新意和构想，主动地寻求、探索和接受信息。这一学习方式和原来的接受型、被动型的学习方式从本质上是不同的。学习方式的转变不仅仅是学习方法的转变 ，还涉及学习习惯、学习态度、学习意识、学习品质等心理因素和心理力量。', 'Papers keywords: virtual reality technology application education environment teaching efficiency\r\n\r\nAbstract: by using computer generated simulation environment, the virtual reality technology of 3d space thoughts can be clearly, make learners direct, naturally and virtual environment in various objects for interaction. Desktop type virtual technology with low cost, easy in education field widely used, it is helpful for creating new teaching environment, strengthening students study main body status. Stimulate the students'' study enthusiasm and creativity, and make the teaching get twice the result with half the effort.\r\n\r\nSince 1980s, multimedia technology, man-machine interface technology, sensing technology and artificial intelligence is supported disciplines such as virtual reality technology rapid development, gradually to infiltrate economy, culture and military and people living, and many other aspects, become a recent international scientific attention a hotspot. Meanwhile, the virtual reality technology also with great speed into teaching, for education development provides a great opportunity. Education undertakings for it, the virtual reality technology can combine the three dimensional space thoughts made it clear that out, can make the learners to direct, naturally and virtual environment in various objects for interaction, and through various forms involved in the events in the process of the development and change of the control, to get a maximum operation and the whole environment of freedom. Therefore, the development of this technology education and training in many areas, has many obvious advantages and characteristics. Virtual reality technology for more rationally applied in education teaching for learners to create more harmonious, the education environment has become a new education research subject.\r\n\r\nOne, the virtual reality technology applied to teaching principles\r\n\r\n(a) promote learning for this, the practical first\r\n\r\nThe so-called virtual reality technology (virtuaI ReaIity, abbreviation VR), is refers to the use of the computer to generate a simulation environment, through a variety of special equipment and user "input" to the environment, with the environment directly realized the user for natural interactive technology; Virtual reality technology to let users who bite the object of the world natural skills investigation or operation, and to provide the seeing, hearing, touching and so on many kinds of visual and natural real-time perception.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology applied in education teaching will promote learners learn the aims, the advanced technology will also serve the teaching needs. Along with the development of virtual reality technology itself has appeared more hierarchical development tendency, according to the interactive and submerged degree of different can be divided into desktop type, tele-immersive, superposition type and virtual reality system four categories. Desktop type of virtual reality technology through relatively cheap hardware generates a real effect, simpler, need devoted cost is not high also, in the education field has a development perspective, easy to popularize. Desktop type virtual reality technology using only personal computers and low-level workstation, put the computer screen as the participant observation a virtual environment, use simple window mouth external equipment (such as: the keyboard, mouse, torque ball, stereo glasses, etc) to rein in a virtual environment and manipulate the virtual objects. Students can in virtual learning environment plays a role, devote yourself to the learning environment, this for their skill training very favorable. Using virtual reality technology, can undertake such as military combat skills, surgical skills, teaching skill, sports skills, car driving skills, electrical maintenance skills, etc. Various kinds of vocational skills training. Because these virtual training system without any danger, learners can practice repeatedly, until master skills so far. Like Beijing university of aeronautics and virtual reality and visualization computer department new technology laboratory in support of national 863 plan, as an integrated units, national university of defense technology, zhejiang university, armored force engineering institute, Chinese academy of sciences software and PLA surveying and mapping colleges, and other units to establish a used for virtual reality technology research and application of the distributed virtual environment foundation information platform (DVENET). In this platform can realize include remote dozens of weapons in the same block lifelike virtual platform for collaborative terrain homework or against drill. Works in personnel (namely users) can through different interactive mode control of real or virtual weapons simulation platform in virtual battle environment for their distributed collaborative and confrontation tactical exercises.\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology to achieve the move to the laboratory piaget "classroom up" ideas and practice, also accord with the constructivist learning theory about "learning is a kind of real situation of experience" point of view.\r\n\r\n(2), applicable in the music for\r\n\r\nTry a virtual reality technology in the teaching of advanced mathematics, requires teachers to find in the teaching design of virtual reality and teaching multi-through-transport and cut people point. Virtual reality technology applied to teaching must be properly. The fact virtual system to develop a demanding, and is not an easy thing, but our teaching and not all the content need with virtual reality technology, can choose from time performance optimization, suit to use the multimedia technology with multimedia, suit to use a virtual reality technology with the virtual reality technology.\r\n\r\nTry in the teaching with virtual reality technology must be moderate, teaching contents and forms must be unified, but must pay attention to leave enough give learners use inappropriate thinking space, instead will make learners immersed in unreal world, difficult to control. Virtual reality has its duality: to one''s senses speaking, it is true that exists; For the constructed object speaking, it is not exist. Therefore, can use this technique imitate many high cost, are dangerous to humans, or have not appeared in real environment is very valuable. For example, "simulation physics laboratory" system, make students could pass personal practice - to do, see, listen to the way of learning. Using the system, students can stop the passage of time, in order to observe carefully spring vibrator at points trajectory changing with time process; Can easily demo and control object of movement as a horizontal cast; But also through the interactive data simulation "let the car along the long plank uniform motion" and other experiments, which profoundly understand physical concept and law. Virtual reality technology applied to teaching is a brand-new topic, not many ready-made experience for reference. But because no experience, because of difficulties, this topic have created space is necessarily unprecedented broad.\r\n\r\nSecond, the virtual reality technology applied to teaching functional advantages\r\n\r\nVirtual reality technology is a computer to produce a man-made empty ran through a variety of special equipment for environmental, allowing the user to sight, hearing, touch, smell and so on many kinds of sensory produce a immersed in the feeling of virtual environment. And the traditional human-machine interaction, virtual reality compared with the three most prominent features: mutuality, immersed sense and imaginative. These characteristics are mainly used in education in following prominent advantage.\r\n\r\n(a) create interactive learning environment, to promote the shift of learning style\r\n\r\nThe new course standard "change the way of that students learn, and actively advocate independently, cooperation, and explore ways of learning, emphasize the students'' active participation and the spirit. Using virtual reality technology computer-generated learning environment, let learners can start from his own viewpoint, use natural skills and some equipment on this formation of virtual world object through and interaction. The technology and methods of conventional not limited screen display device, but multi-channel the human-computer interaction model, let learners feel seemed to leave own locates in the external environment, has real world of immersion in a virtual, become a system component. This study mainly not rely on teacher''s teaching, but rather on the interaction of learners and environment by learners through own feeling, after the thinking and analysis, form target implementation strategies, through the interface system to receive signals, intelligent to feedback, achieve real interaction. This exploratory learning, is more advantageous to the learners perform voluntary construction in the learning. Makes possible from the qualitative and quantitative integrated virtual environment for the perceptual and the rational understanding, then deepening concept, produce originality and conception, actively seek, exploration and receiving information. This study way and original receptive, initiative, passivity, ways of learning from essentially is different. The shift of learning style than just learning method, but also involves the study habits change, learning attitude, learning awareness, learning quality of psychological factors and mental strength. ', '../pic/2011052481886_200891181048979.jpg', '浅谈运用虚拟现实技术创建更和谐的教育环境', 'Discuss with virtual reality technology to create a more harmonious education environment ', '', 15),
(136, 30, '概念设计中的虚拟现实技术工业设计', 'The conceptual design of virtual reality technology industrial design ', 'user12', '2011-05-24', '摘要: 结合工业设计的新方法与新观念，阐述将虚拟现实技术应用于产品概念设计中，加快产品开发的进程，更好地满足市场需求。\r\n关键词:概念设计　虚拟现实技术　产品市场\r\n\r\n一、产品概念设计与市场\r\n\r\n概念设计是工业设计领域中的一个重要方面。国外大公司的产品设计部门包括:1)(Conceptdesign)概念设计;2)(Detaildesign)详细设计;3)(Manufacturingdesign)制造设计。由此可见，产品的概念设计的主导地位和重要性。\r\n\r\n1 概念设计的内涵\r\n\r\n概念的设想是创造性思维的一种体现，概念产品是一种理想化的物质形式。下面以概念设计教学实例之一来说明其涵义:给出一个概念“断药”，让学生进行座椅的开发设计。步骤是，首先向学生讲述心理学中的一个名词———暗示心理，并分别举出一个“安乐死”实验和一个“挽救少女生命”的文学名著故事，从正反两个方面说明暗示对人的健康的影响;然后运用一个“民间故事”阐述如何将“断药”的概念物化到具体的产品上。因为，在民间曾有这样一个说法，就是将一把断了的钥匙用红线穿上挂在小孩的脖子上，取“断钥”的谐音“断药”暗示常生病的孩子挂上“断钥”这挂项链之后，就断了药，从此不再吃药，这也意味着孩子走向健康。所以，将一把断了的钥匙(断药)的概念物化到具体的产品上来为健康做设计时，用折断了的钥匙做椅架为主题，由学生创意出现了形形色色的座椅开发设计方案(其草图、效果图、视图等技术说明从略)，于是就有了一种新型的专用座椅的概念设计。其应用场合为疗养院、医院、不能自理的老人家庭等。\r\n\r\n这是传统的产品概念设计。当然，产品的类型不止是这种无障碍设计思想指导下的专用座椅。产品即人之观念的物化，设计是一种思维行为。在这种思维创造性行为活动中，产品概念的构思是丰富的，人的创作智慧是无穷的。概念产品的类型更是多种多样。\r\n\r\n2 概念设计与产品市场\r\n\r\n完成概念设计只是第一步，能不能进行第二步Detaildesign，第三步Manufacturingdesign，甚至投放市场为开发商或企业带来效益等，这是个风险问题。设计师的概念设计毕竟与难以预料市场变化有着许多差距。如何缩短这一差距，是以往概念设计者的难题。在开发设计的许许多多产品中，只要一百件产品中有几件能够投放市场见效益就是成功。在追求“百分之几”的见效益成功的过程中，如何减少做“分母”的被动，扩大见效益的百分比，仍是最关键的，是公司管理决策人士和设计师共同努力的方向。\r\n\r\n3 虚拟现实技术促使概念设计的市场化\r\n\r\n为了更好地接近产品的市场需求，目前国际上流行的一种“故事版情景预言法”的概念设计，就是将所要开发的产品置于一定的人、时、地、事和物中进行观察、预测、想象和情景分析，其形式是以故事版的平面设计表达展示给人们。于是，产品在设计的开始便多了一份生命和灵气。然而，设计表达在信息时代已是多元化的展示形式，计算机辅助工业设计的发展，尤其是虚拟现实技术在产品概念设计中的应用，已使设计师的设计思路和设计表达如虎添翼;可以想象面对一种虚拟的“故事版情景预言法”设计出的产品，让人更多了一种直观的、亲切的及交互的感受，这样开发设计的产品与传统相比，就大大减少了投放市场的风险性，也为企业决策人寻找商机、判断概念产品能否进一步开发生产，提供更好的依据。虚拟现实技术能模拟整个产品开发过程，保证产品开发一次性成功，加快开发进程，甚至使设计者和用户融为一体，设计出满足市场需要的产品。　　\r\n\r\n二、虚拟现实技术与虚拟产品\r\n\r\n1 虚拟现实系统(VirtualReality，VR)\r\n\r\n虚拟现实系统又称为虚拟现实环境，是指计算机生成的一个实时三维环境。使用者可以在这环境中“自由地”运动，观察周围的景物，还可通过各种专用的传感交互设备与虚拟物体进行交互操作。用户看到的是全彩色景象，听到的是虚拟环境中的音响，感觉(手、脚或皮肤等)到的是虚拟环境所反馈的作用力，从而让使用者产生一种身临其境的感觉。产生虚拟现实环境的方法有:\r\n1)基于模型的方法(ModelbasedMethod， MM)这种方法产生虚拟环境的步骤为:\r\n①用放置在不同地点的多个摄像机将某环境或事物记录下来;\r\n②利用计算机的视频技术抽取出环境或事物的三维模型;\r\n③从虚拟摄像头的视角展示获得模型。具体的做法是:获得数据→标度摄像头→分离对象→建立模型→嵌入颜色→交互回放。\r\n2)基于图像的方法(ImagebasedMethod， IM)一般做法是:\r\n用摄像头连续扫描周围空间来获取某一区域完整的景物图像，将获取的景物图像，通过图像处理技术，按坐标映射到图形工作站的虚拟全景屏上，用户载上头盔显示器就可以看到所摄周围景物环境。\r\n\r\n2 虚拟现实系统的常用设备及要求\r\n\r\n虚拟现实系统常用设备有:三维鼠标(也称鸟标)、数据手套、数据衣、头盔显示器、立体声耳机等。对虚拟现实系统的要求除了应具有高性能的计算机系统(包括软、硬件)外，还必须有下列关键技术提供强有力的支持:(1)能以实时的速度生成具有三维全色彩的、有明暗、有阴影、有纹理的、逼真感强的景物图像;(2)头盔显示器能产生高分辨率图像和较大的视角;(3)能高精度地实时跟踪用户的头和手;(4)能对用户的动作产生力学反馈。\r\n\r\n3 虚拟产品(VirtualProduct，VP)\r\n\r\n虚拟产品是虚拟现实技术应用于产品设计的产物，是一个数字化的产品。它具有真实产品所必须具有的特征。通过对产品实时性功能的仿真，设计人员或用户就能够像使用真实产品一样使用虚拟产品。由于产品的设计过程是数字化的，因此节省了传统方法中需要制造的物理模型(包括概念模型、模拟实验模型、外观模型和生产模型等)的时间和物质。在计算机中由于对设计的产品进行反复设计、分析、干涉检查、模具设计等过程，使设计绘图的工作量比传统的绘图工作量大大减少。　　\r\n\r\n三、虚拟现实技术在概念设计中应用前景　　\r\n\r\n在概念设计中，如采用头脑风暴法进行方案创意时，可以将体验设计思想更好地融于其中，也就是更多地关注产品使用者的感受，而非产品本身。比如，针对不同用户及爱好者的要求，在不同的虚拟环境中，让他们亲自体验修改模型的感受;利用触摸屏来选择产品的造型、色彩、装饰风格等许多可选部件。在渲染和生成十分逼真的三维模型时，充分感受了自己所喜爱的产品在虚拟环境中的“真实”情况。甚至还可根据用户的建议，邀请部分用户直接与设计者一起对模型提出修改意见，观察设计和修改过程，直至大多数人满意为止。\r\n\r\n为了适应激烈的市场竞争，设计厂家不能坐等用户找上门订购产品，而应该主动把自己厂家的产品推向市场。利用虚拟现实技术做出虚拟产品的动画广告，再与计算机网络技术结合起来，使用户能够通过网络来游览设计厂家的设计产品，并能直接在虚拟环境中对产品的功能、结构、外形、色彩等方面进行实时交互、了解、观察;同时，还可以通过Email对产品提出意见和建议，让厂家参照各方面的意见修改和完善所设计的产品。这样可提高设计厂家的竞争力，为设计厂家谋得更多的市场份额。\r\n\r\n若用户对厂家设计的产品引起购买的欲望，通过网上游览，将信息反馈到各商家，商家则会主动争先与厂家联系，网上定货，使厂家的产品提前占领市场。由于激烈的全球市场竞争，各国都投入了大量的资金对虚拟现实技术及其在工业设计领域中的应用进行深入地研究。将研究的成果及时转化为生产力，这是产品迅速占领市场的关键。\r\n\r\n参　考　文　献\r\n1　陈军等 虚拟现实中虚拟景象产生的技术初探 计算机应用研究，1999，6\r\n2　熊曼辰等 数字化与概念化工业设计 ICME2000论文集\r\n3　孙守迁等 计算机辅助概念设计研究现状和发展趋势 中国机械工程，1999(10)\r\n4　王玉新等 三维虚拟设计环境下机械产品的概念设计 第一届国际机械工程学术会议论文，2000', 'Abstract: the new method of combined industrial design with new ideas, this paper expounds the application of virtual reality technology in to product conceptual design, speed up product development process and better meet the market demand.\r\n\r\nKeywords: the conceptual design of virtual reality technology product market\r\n\r\nA, product conceptual design and the market\r\n\r\nConcept design in the field of industrial design is an important part. Foreign big company product design department include: 1) (Conceptdesign) concept design; 2) (detailed design Detaildesign); 3) (Manufacturingdesign) manufacturing design. Therefore, the product conceptual design of the dominant position and importance.\r\n\r\n1 the conceptual design connotation\r\n\r\nConcept scenario is a reflection of creative thinking, conceptual product is a kind of utopian corporeal form. Here in conceptual design teaching examples to illustrate its meaning: one gives a concept "break the medicine", let the student the development design undertake seat. To the students, the first step is one of about psychology -- implied psychology, noun and separate cite an "euthanasia" experiment and a "save the girl life" the literary classics story from negative aspects that hinted that affecting the health of people; Then use a "folk stories," explains how to "break the medicine" concept materialized to specific products. Because, the folk had such a statement, is the key to a broken with red lines put on hanging in the neck, take "break the harmonics" key "broken medicine" implies often sick child key "hung" break after the hang necklace he expired medicine, never take medicine, it also means that the child to health. So, will a broken key (breaking the concept of medicine) chemical to specific products for health do come up with design, broken key theme, make chair frame by students'' creative appeared all kinds of seat development design scheme (its sketches, rendering, view, etc CongLve) technical specifications, so there will be a new kind of special seat concept design. Its applications for nursing homes, hospitals, and the old man cannot provide family.\r\n\r\nThis is the traditional product conceptual design. Of course, the type of product is not just the barrier-free design guidance of special seat. The concept of product, chemical, design is a kind of thinking behavior. In this kind of thinking creativity activity, product conception is rich, the person''s creative wisdom is infinite. Concept of various types of more products.\r\n\r\n2 the conceptual design and product market\r\n\r\nFinish the conceptual design is only the first step, can Detaildesign second step, the third step Manufacturingdesign, even on the market for developers or enterprise to bring benefit etc, it is a risk. The designer''s concept design after all and unpredictable market change has many gap. How to shorten the gap, is the problem of previous concept designer. In the development and design of many products, as long as 100 products in the few can put on the market see benefits is to succeed. In the pursuit of "the few" percent see benefits in the process of success, how to reduce the denominator "do" passive, expand see benefits percentage, is still the most critical, is the company management decision personage and designers of the common efforts of direction.\r\n\r\n3 virtual reality technology impels the conceptual design of marketization\r\n\r\nIn order to better close to product market demand, the international fashion a "story edition scene the concept of" prophecy method to design, is the development of products in certain people, and, when that land, carries on the observation, forecasting, imagination and scene analysis, its form is with storyboards graphic design expression shows to people. Then, the product is designed begins a many life and spirit. However, the design expression in the information era, is already diversified display form, computer-aided industrial design development, especially the virtual reality technology application in product conceptual design, has made the designer''s way of thinking and the design expression; mora. Can imagine facing a virtual "story edition scene prophecy method" product design, let a person more an intuitive, friendly and interactive experience, such development and design of products, compared with traditional market greatly reduces the risk of the enterprise, but also for policy-makers to seek business opportunities, judge whether further development concept product production, providing better basis. Virtual reality technology can simulate the whole product development process, guarantee product development success at one time, speed up development process, even to enable the designer and the user is an organic whole, design the meet the needs of the market of product.\r\n\r\nSecond, the virtual reality technology and virtual products\r\n\r\n1 virtual reality system (VirtualReality, VR)\r\n\r\nVirtual reality system called virtual reality environment, refers to computer generated a real-time 3d environment. Users can in this environment of "free" movement, observe the surrounding scenery, but also by various specialized sensor interactive devices and virtual objects on interactive operation. Users see is full-color picture, hear is the sound and feel of virtual environment (hands, feet or skin, etc.) to is a virtual environment, thus let the force feedback from users to produce a experience personally feeling. Create a virtual reality environmental methods are:\r\n\r\n1) model based method (ModelbasedMethod, MM) this method to create a virtual environment for: the steps\r\n\r\n(1) placed in different places with multiple cameras will record a environment or things;\r\n\r\n(2) the video technology using computer abstracted from the environment or 3d model of things;\r\n\r\n(3) the perspective from virtual camera show get model. Particular way is: get data - scale cameras - separation object - model - embedded color - interactive playback.\r\n\r\n2) based on image method (ImagebasedMethod, IM) the general method is:\r\n\r\nUse camera to obtain continuous scan surrounding space a regional complete scenery scenery, will obtain image image, through image processing technology, according to coordinate mapping to the graphics workstations virtual panoramic screen, user load a helmet display can see the scenery around environmental perturbation.\r\n\r\n2 virtual reality system commonly used equipment and requirements\r\n\r\nVirtual reality system commonly used equipment is: 3d mouse (also called bird standard), data glove, data clothing, helmets monitor, stereo headphones, etc. Virtual reality system requirements of high except should have computer system (including software and hardware) outside, still must have the following key technology to provide powerful support: (1) to generate 3d real-time speed with the whole color, light and shade, a shadow, a texture, BiZhenGan strong scenery image; (2) helmets monitor can produce high resolution image and larger perspective; (3) can accurately real-time tracking user''s head and hands; (4) can produce mechanics of user action feedback.\r\n\r\n3 VirtualProduct, virtual product (VP)\r\n\r\nVirtual product is virtual reality technology applied to product design product, is a digital products. It has real product must have characteristics. Based on the simulation, real-time functional product design or the user can like using the real product use virtual product as. Because the product design process is digital, so save the traditional method needs to make physical model (including a conceptual model, a simulation model, exterior model and the production model, etc.) of time and material. In computers because of the product design and design, analysis, interference, mould design process, which makes the design drawing workload than traditional graphics workload is greatly reduced.\r\n\r\nThree, virtual reality technology in the concept design application prospect\r\n\r\nIn concept design, if use brainstorming method for the scheme can be creative experience design thought, better into them, also is the more attention to product the user feel, and not the product itself. For example, according to different users and lovers requirement, in different virtual environment, let them personally experience modified model feelings; Using the touch screen to select a product modelling, colour, decoration style and many other optional components. In the rendering and generate very lifelike 3d model, fully feel their favorite products in the "real" virtual environment. Even can according to user''s suggestion, invited some users to model directly with designer together, amendment opinions obserational design and modification process, until most people feel satisfied.\r\n\r\nIn order to adapt to the fierce market competition, design manufacturers can''t wait for users find ordering the product, but should also actively put himself manufacturer product to market. Using virtual reality technology to make virtual product animation advertising, again with computer network technology, users can combine through network to visit design manufacturer, and can design products directly on the virtual environment of the product, the function, structure and appearance, the color and so on aspects of real-time interactive, understanding, observation; At the same time, but also through the Email to product the Suggestions and opinions, let manufacturers refer to all views to modify and improve the design of the product. Which can improve the competitiveness of design for designing factory get more manufacturers of market share.\r\n\r\nIf the user to the manufacturer to design products purchase desire, caused by an electronic tour, the information feedback to each merchants, the businessman will contact with manufacturer, active scrambling online orders, make the product of manufacturer of occupy the market in advance. Because the fierce competition of the global market, nations have spent a great deal of money on virtual reality technology and its application in industrial design in-depth study. Will the research achievement timely into productivity, and this is the key products are rapidly occupation of the market.\r\n\r\nAnd exam rodman offered\r\n\r\n1 j in virtual reality such as virtual scene produce technical asain computer application and research, 1989,134\r\n\r\n2 XiongManChen etc ICME2000 digital and conceptual industrial design workshop\r\n\r\n3 SunShouQian etc computer aided conceptual design research situation and development trend of Chinese mechanical engineering, 1999 (10)\r\n\r\n4 WangYuXin etc 3d virtual design environment mechanical product conceptual design the first international mechanical engineering academic conference papers, 2000 ', '../pic/2011052464981_2007618104731674.jpg', '概念设计中的虚拟现实技术工业设计', 'The conceptual design of virtual reality technology industrial design ', '', 34);

